"enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Fer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWZSzyJiEb1fDvsnWs7I8Pd-gxtFI-uThgsuOgpa_5ufOMYxdDZgg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My husband and I feel so fortunate to have found Austin Dental Works, and we absolutely recommend their services!\nAfter trying out several different dentists across the Austin area, we finally found our \"dental home\" here about four years ago and haven't looked back since.\nThe entire staff is consistently friendly, welcoming, and knowledgeable, making every visit—from a simple cleaning to more complex work—a smooth and stress-free experience.\nA special shout-out to Dr. Jaros, who is truly in a league of her own. She is incredibly patient and has such wonderful manners. She never rushes through an appointment; instead, she takes the time to thoroughly answer and clarify every single question we have with genuine understanding. It’s so rare to find a doctor who makes you feel heard and comfortable.\nIf you’re looking for a team that truly cares about both your smile and your peace of mind, this is the place to go. We can’t think of a better practice to trust with our dental health.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nicole Contero","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ1UlkHHotAqkeHUKcdyxRwOhyk5VuwfOGZlR36QBXZ-NAVSQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I LOVE the team at Austin Dental Works! They have been taking care of my dental health for several years, and I recommend them all the time. The staff is incredibly friendly, comforting and professional. Dr. Jaros makes understanding my dental health approachable and not intimidating.\n\nADW is super easy to book and communicate with, and Tiffanie ensures all the insurance/financial questions are covered.\n\nThanks for all y’all do!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Teresa Thy Le","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVYOTWKGFoPifucPs9qaiKti1idNh_Gs7OO-mB2pEKNoFiJFCa8FA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Staff is amazing!!! Tiffanie, Valentina and Dr. Jaros were all kind, informative and professional. I loved my experience and felt at ease the entire duration of my visit. They did not make me feel anxious one bit and the process was very transparent and easy-going. I would highly recommend Austin Dental Works for your dental care needs!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Anuj Bellare","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVBF08O3Lrmv6lxryc95tNL4h69AendaH9NtrYKFExHxivcYoUF=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have only been through 3 appointment - an introductory appointment, dental cleaning and cavity filing + crown prep. The experience has been great until now. Everyone here has been super friendly. Dr Jaros is clearly skilled at dentistry, explaining every step of the process. She also often asks how you are doing which is very comforting. Nobody in the world ever said “I look forward to my next dental appointment” but this place comes close to making you feel that way. 😊","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tanya Embers","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocItKPJ4nNafLE0GFEg3A5sVgnB7ghhpKCA_5er2leztIt532g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love Austin Dental Works! The staff is so lovely and kind, and Dr Jaros is a great dentist. Always can trust their recommendations and care. They never try to sell you more than you need and are super easy to schedule with.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Todd McDougall","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJVUCq3mTlAT5-fMdHzKuhIsoXbZ43DbfNGjSS0Mun0A2WMfQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Austin Dental Works has been my dentist for over 5 years now. The staff is super friendly and head Dentist is excellent.  They also give free whitening every 6 months!  Romans 10:9","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alicia Lewis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIUjDWWr9emtJAQ7xjR6Q_vBX7iIn9J2fO7hBa4MX78t5dCyA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best dentist I’ve had and you never have to wait. They schedule people perfectly so you are in and out. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Joni Buschow","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWDG-npJ_DwGtusTPY5YovhzYO1CPJ3JFId-9kKk-1XefYOqWM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr Lindsey Jaros' expertly found a dental issue that was unseen by my last dentist. Her expertise to resolve this issue improved my health \u0026 well-being. Her staff is amazing: kind, helpful,\u0026 friendly.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
