ments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Becky Cook","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV7fb8ICrs7A1kdjkkonHD6hQl-6Nwe_LFILH_WgMGcBVsHfa25=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I took my dad in for a consultation with Dr. Meek, and the experience was outstanding. His staff was extremely friendly and welcoming. Dr. Meek was amazing—he took the time to thoroughly explain all of our options and made sure we fully understood everything. He even came out to visit with me personally while my dad was receiving his treatment. We felt truly cared for every step of the way.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cii Anderson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXgWl5OH24rSTQeU0e2qehPTdHhseHePxhTsrvq_BDJSEWP91o=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I went to 38th Street Dental today for my X-rays and cleaning, and this was my very first visit — and wow, what an experience. I had the absolute pleasure of being taken care of by Regina and Dr. David Tasch, and they truly rocked today.\n\nI typically have extreme dental anxiety, but from the moment I walked in, I felt calm, heard, and comfortable. Regina was so kind, patient, and gentle, explaining everything along the way and making sure I was okay. Dr. Tasch was just as amazing — professional, reassuring, and thorough without ever making me feel rushed or overwhelmed.\n\nThis visit completely changed how I feel about going to the dentist. The environment was welcoming, the care was top-tier, and my anxiety was basically nonexistent — which says a LOT. I’m genuinely grateful for such a positive first experience and couldn’t recommend this office, Regina, and Dr. Tasch enough.\n\nThe front office staff were nice as well. They are the face of the office. Getting that warm welcome feeling upon check in and check out is amazing and makes you want to return, especially when it’s your first visit. I didn’t catch their names,\nbut they rocked.\n\nIf you’re nervous about dental visits, this is absolutely the place to go.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jenny G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVdmjqnc8gtEupK2Cg03SE6uMnq9soCAdS6454OxlYCFyaWAQHR=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A very amazing and friendly place. They do thorough and gentle teeth cleaning. No more sore gums after cleaning. The stuff is friendly  patient, and easy to talk to. Waiting time is always minimal.\nThey do charge more so they can focus on providing high quality services rather than selling extra things to you. But it is so worth it. Highly recommend this place.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Steve Demarest","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVWzJLu8mPkCdlHfMquddJ61zyaUycCiufn17d4JyfWaBrZb5c=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"There are many good things about this practice. First and foremost the quality of the treatment seems very high. My results have been good. I also like the way the office is run in terms of very minimal wait times - I’m usually in the chair within a minute or two of my appointment time, and for simple cleaning sessions you can be in and out in less than 30 mins.  My one improvement point is a lack of flexibility on appointment times, which are booked 6 months in advance. If you need to move the time or day closer in  they are forced to shift you out a month or more even if you contact them a week in advance with a requested change.  My last appointment I spent about 2 mins with the Dr - it seems like there would be more flexibility.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kristina Grad","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUG4eShlEwR-vS2r0fI4I1vSvtJEY3Oap9uwHNsrjQcQ3gimKg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an amazing experience here - I truly felt taken care of above and beyond. The entire team is so kind, professional, and welcoming, and the office itself is beautiful and calming. You can really tell they care about their patients. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sonja Thomas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUmHCJKA_OOHMrPyUyDom-rrT31mh8ZvbF8a3kB-wvhx1w3qaTjYQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Walking in the door you feel like family. Everyone greets you like they really missed you over the past 6 months.\nEach professional is skilled in their area. They make visiting the dentist office a pleasure.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"mglunday","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK5NJCo1x2Kqk31d96ili71SZPhhNK2obF70ft51T1k8_emzQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Visiting from Phoenix and had an issue with one of my teeth.  They were able to schedule me in within 24hrs to be seen.  They were by far the most thorough and professional team I have ever encountered.   They listened to my concerns, explained everything in detail, and provided a referral for possible root canal.   I am so appreciative and will move my dental care from Phoenix to Austin.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sylvia Kellner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIaJ200TlCey-oqvbAjMNdooXnZYwwOsp97V1dKS83zA2TdCg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have searched a long time for a good dentist and Dr Meek  and his staff are definitely at the top Of recommendations. They were very professional, gentle and kind . It’s hard to find sincerity, and dedication","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
