ergency services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"crowd","name":"Crowd","options":[{"name":"LGBTQ+ friendly","enabled":true},{"name":"Transgender safespace","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Checks","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Sara Kora","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIrG87kk9xTfHPlmrjGfRX5s-afZ2YXZPZjUgB7SBdhzv37lg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a wonderful experience at Lady Bird Dental. The team were welcoming and professional from the moment I walked in. The doctor was very good, friendly, and  knowledgeable. They took the time to explain everything clearly and made us feel comfortable and cared for. I truly appreciate the kindness and patience they showed. I highly recommend Lady Bird Dental to anyone looking for excellent dental care!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Darnah Mercieca","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUwZhqRjF7XYZB4SHyejTO3CO_Y3QDnlFNKdK2uW0m_W8oH4Pw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have truly appreciated the care I’ve received at Lady Bird Dental. I’ve been going to Dr. Dudeen for the past few years for cleanings, exams, and he replaced a filling. He’s super friendly and always remembers key details about your life, even though I only see him a couple times a year. All the staff are lovely and helpful, and their clinic is clean and inviting. Thanks for looking after my smile!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Logan Bowser","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIvGyh9oIoNE2R6jukcRRWY4BcAuNmyjlh8-gNFBXh5Q2YgtdE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Have always been hesitant to go to the dentist and always avoided it. However, my experience at LBD has dramatically improved how I view going to the dentist. The staff at the front are the most personable and hilarious people which would ease anyone’s anxiety. The hygienist that I’ve seen twice now is fantastic: Always quick and gentle while she also makes genuine conversation. The dentist is very nice, thorough, and was happy to answer my questions.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Karol M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ5gAjB5sXl-0TCyEYkEDoAhA7CpWe1mrCt1OiqgY5HnntWXQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Such a friendly group! Had a great appointment with Dr. Dudeen for cosmetic work. He has great attention to detail and you can tell he cares about getting you the best result. Glad I found this place!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hannah Schafer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV8pd-W7u27CF49_Qg21loz1J7RJOoGrGswoESQwLr0NBNVE_fF9g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been to a lot of dentist offices over the years, and this one is by far the nicest. The entire staff is so sweet and friendly, and they make every visit feel comfortable. The dentist is always fair, approachable, and takes the time to listen to any concerns I have before and during treatment. I really appreciate the care and attention they put into making sure I feel at ease. I highly recommend them!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kristen Sedillo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL1tYdYP69gTJQg0CYqE1_EcV1Jk41eax-A27cNkz-8m_xtF6A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Dudeen is the best dentist I’ve ever had! From the front office staff to his hygienists, they all know me by name. The service is impeccable! In the past year I’ve had wisdom teeth pulled, whitening, cleanings, and a successful Invisalign journey. So happy with my results! Always recommend a Lady Bird Dental’s team!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kaitlin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWKJ5nbUU8pCyH-MhuruqrKhkr31cNUo1SU3MZ7G8eppAZaSu4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It had been four years since I’d been in a dentist’s office. Of course, I felt anxiety and shame about it as an adult. When filling out the forms online, I was honest about everything—anxiety, finances, work schedule, you name it. All of it had kept me from getting to the dentist. But I finally wanted to go in because I had four cavities right in the front of my mouth, on display for everyone to see.\nI knew I had to find a dentist first, and after opening multiple different options on Google Maps, I found Lady Bird Dental. They even had a special for first-time patients: X-rays and a cleaning for $99. I ended up having to call and reschedule as soon as they opened due to an emergency, and Kathy quickly offered me an appointment for the following day.\nToday was my appointment. Alexis welcomed me in, and Sara took me back. Sara talked with me—she engages with authenticity and a warmth that can really help calm nerves. We joked that my blood pressure would be high because my anxiety was, and sure enough, whew. She took my X-rays and talked me through them.\nEnter Dr. Dudeen. His tone of voice is gentle, and his demeanor is respectful and kind. He delivered my dental assessment in an honest, polite, and nonjudgmental manner. He even told me he could take care of the four cavities in the front today—at my very first appointment. I couldn’t believe the words coming out of his mouth.\nAlexis came back in and helped me find the best payment route possible so I could get the fillings done. Alexis stayed with me to make sure I could find a financial route best for me.  Dr. Dudeen did an incredible job on them—precise, efficient, and caring. Paz assisted him, and when she handed me a mirror, I finally got to look. Tears of joy began streaming down my face. Paz handed me a box of tissues and she gave me a moment to just be.\nI’m overwhelmed with gratitude, joy, and pride walking out of Lady Bird Dental today. The staff truly couldn’t be better—all the way around. I know where I’ll be trusting and following up with my dental health needs from now on. I’m scheduling as soon as my new insurance kicks in.\nI highly recommend checking out Lady Bird Dental.\nIf you live with anxiety, depression, shame, or fears of the dentist, I encourage you to fill out the forms honestly and check this place out. They care enough to read your forms, support you through it, and meet you where you are.\n\nY’all- thank you so much. Sincerely. Thank you.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Haydn James","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKAEfvcXFrpFhDjyKksvh_q2NvPoB5M540zfhAJOZd8xjyViQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Attended Lady Bird Dental in Austin as a patient today. The paperwork was easy to complete and the friendly staff at the front and in the back made the experience a joy. Dr. Dudeen was great and fully explained everything as he went. Couldn’t be happier.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
