coXjm7w0VS_frwQr2Sd61KKNRIoYNB2oW8ck71zRdUiIFSMOZATG1KLSRp_BbpBkJZUlb7nOFNLDmuoSigrPJr5Hzot-fVKCre5WYBW2d40=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn016Vya3GswxZjmNZhbHc4UclflBkwjxngrqhwS1atNNJG9WQV2yrWeiUQS2apHLUnSBV0A_vFwi-3a5_VbbmIaWQryhd6n2qzKNZaH75PSgFSieJzDEMJxfJ8qe17u-m6f-yu24l5r54Pn=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2VybEZ_BLfgllz2JRizU9NhkcGWQamjaR13Ga-fAtGJ7J-HlK05RqjhlRyCPVdFMYKCUHKV0Fg0WaBDTwGsF-A_I9VKnVPrghqBGrgjLGfUYOdykzejAzfriKSdHNJ7-UkOQwAyC8oiRGE=k-no"],"When":"2025-6-26"},{"Name":"Lauren Hargraves","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJQbg1S2k0rD0EkEfNLw1XSLD3_jB7TOfxjLuFs_2mtGZ91eJA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Yesterday was my first time an Enamel Dentistry on Parmer, and I had the most wonderful experience ever at any dental office. The office is really modern and cozy, and everyone from the front desk staff to the tech as well as my actual doctor were incredibly friendly. I came in as a new patient and was there just to get my regular screening and exam, but the dentist, Serena, and tech, Carla, listened to my hopes and concerns genuinely. They ended up identifying some things they could do right then and spent the morning in treatment with me. They were honest and transparent, even when it came to the Treatment Payment Specialist giving me a breakdown of expenses as well as financing options - no pressure whatsoever to do anything. Jennifer and Carla were very personable and made me feel as comfortable as possible. They use some really neat and innovative technology, and provided me with detailed information and access to my records immediately which was noce. Definitely will be sticking around and continuing to go here!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vi Vo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVQ8dt2GWlVuQZebzo-8Udm7mrm2sQTFA4ecOpsV9Sx9CnQZtVB=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I can’t say enough great things about this dental office! From the moment I walked in, the staff made me feel welcomed and at ease. The front desk was friendly and efficient, and I never felt rushed or like “just another patient.”\n\nThe dentist took the time to explain everything clearly, answered all of my questions, and made sure I was comfortable throughout the entire visit. I really appreciated their gentle approach during the cleaning and treatment—honestly, it was the most relaxed I’ve ever felt in a dental chair!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dave Threlkeld","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocISnHKDEXTxgpqbezw6EEn4lBT8sgnMuQutremrthcfAa1bYg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My first experience with them was a marathon session of emergency work and I'm so glad I found them in time! I was impressed by their thoroughness and their consideration of the patient's comfort meant a great deal. I recommended someone to them later that afternoon as the anesthetic was wearing off. Doctor Mauven and the staff are worth a look if you are searching for your new dentist. Good people and good caregivers.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kennia Cobos","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKmohSFCxl6xHcqPbp0C8OePZA9CGmhiSdsGCoKH_aCXuLcPA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The staff always greet you with a smile and make you feel right at home. Our dentist goes above and beyond to answer any questions I may have about my Childrens dental health.\n\nI absolutely don’t mind waiting in the lobby as it’s always welcoming and clean; it’s a relaxing, nice atmosphere… and the coffee bar is a plus!\n\nWe always a pleasant experience, I would recommend Enamel Dentistry to anyone!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Su Rodriguez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK0ldIaeGIhYUfiI_6tgOL1bBtG_ePDot_N50IYV3jngnkcFw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Always had a great experience here! First time going to the dentist in 10 years and they made me feel welcomed. Also had my wisdom teeth extracted with this surgeon that comes in on Fridays and that was also a great experience !","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"AaLiiyah Zsanaee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVvB-UkZusz0S-i3Xd-2TJmdOx9B7MM9Q9xpbC2imyinO2x2IS5=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First visit as a new patient and they took very good care of me. Excited for my next visit. 1 step closer to a better smile","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Taliyah Ramey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKzlT8Pd1tFpDMfUUYwM2gwvPVSkUPMBeC3H04zyl3L1NKSwA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"l've visited this location a few times in the past \u0026 had ok experiences: very informative, nice clean offices. Unfortunately, yesterday I did not have a good experience. I traveled an hour to come to this dentist for more x-rays and to see if I could get an earlier appointment than what I already have at a different dentist. They took over an hour to do the X-rays and exams, gave me a $4000+ estimate, just for me to call to schedule \u0026 their new dentist refusing to allow me to set an appointment. She claimed there was another issue that she recommends for me to take care of first but this is simply her opinion. When I asked if this was a recommendation or requirement, she could not give me an answer. I had to ask 4 or 5 times for her to finally say she would not complete the work.\nShe even suggested that I get a second opinion when they were the second opinion! No other dentist has shared any of these concerns, even at the same exact office she works in. They wasted my time and I also wasted a visit that will go towards my insurance.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
