coming environment where they know you and prioritize patient connection,  while at the same time being current in best dental practices. I no longer live in South Austin, but I make the drive to South Austin Dentist because I know I am well cared for there.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"craig bligh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJBL8Y5oHfmNsqIRjHbzEkJ8u1jzj57y24c72xSoyGx5BjCXw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Van Wicklen and his team at South Austin Dentist are kind, efficient, professional and highly skilled. Jamie, my dental hygienist, is the best. They offer pragmatic advice on dental care; I do not feel they are trying sell products and services that are not necessary. I highly recommend South Austin Dentist, they get a 10 out of 10 in my opinion based on my experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Yvonne G.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIMKGc4goDzVFGOE7txNMTyITop9Ta5TT4qwjL9TTQ4WETU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"High quality service. Jamie, my dental hygienist, is thorough and I value her friendship. The front office is professional, and Dr. Steven Van Wicklin uses modern dental techniques for a smooth visit.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sam Avila","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJlryuqPS1Eq1uC9lpbMk1H8rTVxm9FRKKKH30fKBWdEC53=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Before I started coming to South Austin Dentist I never looked forward to a dental visit. But since my first visit there I look forward to it. Everyone from the front desk to the dental hygienist to the dentist is wonderful and thanks to them I no longer dread my dental visits. I highly recommend them.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Elizabeth O'Brien","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK1gtdLmm6jWJA9gKs7vjdQg0soL9DFfAGdY6WU6p6HGkup3VY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best dentist in town: Steven van Wicklen: skilled, calm, warm and friendly. We’ve been loyal customers for many years. And Jamie, the dental hygienist, is extremely thorough—and fun…great personality!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tom Jenkinson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXW6FdB5CdX6RbAtxfN6ja3mHa3hK8m_m0n68M5KTDzLA9ruPvwwQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Steven Van Wicklin, the best kept dentist secrete in south Austin and his team of assistamts, dental hygenists and top notch office manager, are simply fantastic. You will be listened to, assesed, taken care of, and treated with expert clinical care while receiving the best dental outcomes.\nBeen going to Dr.  for decades. Call his office and ask for an appointment and check him out.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Raquelle Godbey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUabGqj0keNGkqOTjWoL578KWBVA8hlpYG95nN9_coFONJOMQc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been a patient with Dr Van Wicklen since around 1988, and have had a range of dental work performed over the years, all excellently. This dental office is the most pleasant and comfortable I have been to. The professional staff is so friendly and committed to patient service and comfort.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Laura Havlick","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXhLkJDN2rf-WEh4tNESg6H-QId8TxOTYEi2446DQPdxUjOO6PJ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This dentist was a very welcome change from my previous two dental groups!  My previous dentist had gotten too busy and not responsive to my questions/concerns, and was pushing me to get major dental work.  After I left them and signed up for new insurance that better covered my needs, my 2nd previous dentist overcharged me and also said I needed major dental work.  Then I went to UT Health Sci Ctr in SA, but they were too far for me.  Finally, I checked Yelp for a nearby dentist and found this one (South Austin Dentist) who has been a dentist for about 30 years and was highly recommended. He was wonderful — welcoming, knowledgeable, reassuring, and available for not only a consultation but a quick sealing of exposed gums at short notice.  He’s my dentist now!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
