ayments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Narrie Moye","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVKrwhjwpGvZefU4I4xaW-Ho-3657u50YuYJoRLQaBo_Pi0uz5c=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Harger is the best! He's been my dentist for the last 19 years. I moved way South Austin back in 2013 and I will still make the drive because I do not wish to see anyone else. He provides great care and has patience. Highly highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Megan Hagins","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLpqHXMiqyD80oH5SZcCBhb4I5pBSKc5HC4nFj0uXYqLX0G2w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I started going to Shoal Creek when I needed an emergency crown on a cracked tooth last summer (2025) and received excellent care. I just returned for a 6 moth teeth cleaning and had the best, most gentle but thorough cleaning experience of my life. Thanks, Jennifer Egan! No more white knuckles for me!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"L B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLavBqDfjecuChi2NhABqwyval7vVenJTkvxIXFPjYaB5_3pA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My husband and I are both patients of Dr. Harger at Shoal Creek Dental. Hubby had an appointment today with Leo (who is the best hygienist ever!) for a cleaning.\n\nCoincidentally, I had a crown come off last evening. I called Shoal Creek Dental and left a message to ask if it would be possible to have the crown repaired during the time my husband was in his appointment.\n\nI got a call bright and early this morning to say they had time to see me and to come on in.\n\nThank you, Dr. Harger, Leslie, Juliana, Jessica, and Leo. We so appreciate all of you❣️","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Scott Saunders","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW9RP7U6HTW-lgDkD01Uuz8Zjj6VYc-cN4Kob3PCkknqax-tyCd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love Shoal Creek Dental, my wife and I have been going there for years. They are friendly, on time, respectful of patient choice, and conscious of costs. I would highly recommend Dr Grimm at Shoal Creek Dental!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ali Smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUFgdw-RhFcExr6sBY_vtf9IrXcs82GbTm5Rq-5WR2QhQem3KI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been going to SCDC “Dr Jenkins” from 1976 until he retired. I miss him!  He left behind a great staff. Jennifer  Egan has been my primary hygienist for the last 20 years. The team,  technology and services provided has transformed significantly since 1976, their commitment to provide exceptional care continues. I no longer live in Austin, but for me personally they are worth the drive  Here’s a big shout out to Jennifer!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Charlie Angulo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV8u7uQ0Wa8jlU84fBLbVb9yzynfDh4ncdYhKGW3JYXhvzl1bck=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I can't recommend Shoal Creek Dental Care enough! After skipping dental visits for a while, I was quite nervous about going back, but my experience here has been fantastic. The staff is incredibly friendly and welcoming, which immediately put me at ease.\n\nI've had regular cleanings, and each time, the hygienists have been thorough yet gentle. They took the time to explain everything they were doing and made sure I was comfortable throughout the process.\n\nI also decided to get Invisalign, and the team has been amazing in guiding me through the entire process. They answered all my questions and made sure I understood what to expect, which really helped alleviate my anxiety.\n\nShoal Creek Dental truly cares about their patients and provides exceptional care.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Robert Perez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKbkaHLs0kLDr9wYF40e2NZLnp3B2Y4L6Ec8agCccK6-eGwLQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Superb dentist.  My crown fell out on a Saturday morning.  I met him at his office that same morning and he re-inserted it.  Saved my weekend.  Superb caring service.   Robert","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tamara S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWhqFqvZvJ2mOw43KuLz4_ZRjPZaY931Ho7Jmjee2HrwslVcvwxaw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely love this dental office. The staff is always so warm and inviting and kind. Dr. Grimm is amazing and truly a unicorn of the dental world. She is an incredible wealth of knowledge \u0026 experience. I highly recommend Dr. Grimm and this office. We’ve had the absolute best experience.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
