e":"Cosmetic dentistry","enabled":true},{"name":"Emergency services","enabled":true},{"name":"Pediatric care","enabled":true},{"name":"Sedation dentistry","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Gender-neutral restroom","enabled":true},{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"crowd","name":"Crowd","options":[{"name":"LGBTQ+ friendly","enabled":true},{"name":"Transgender safespace","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Checks","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking garage","enabled":true},{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Free street parking","enabled":true},{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Gina R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKQLGDgY_ZSTDlndjsCoW3BHv4v9FTvhiQPE1O3rhjzVfK7lw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently returned to Enamel Dentistry on South Lamar for my four month follow up and the level of care I received once again was exceptional. Everyone on the team was professional, friendly, and made me feel comfortable from the moment I arrived. Danielle at the front desk, providing such a kind and heartwarming welcome back; Alan who retook my scans, was cautious and prompt with his task. Alex who is an amazing and thorough dental assistant consistently asking if I was comfortable during my procedure. Ms. Miranda who assisted with my insurance plan before I checked out, made sure my appointment and dental packet was provided to me before I left.  Dr. Celia Rathmell undoubtedly took the time to explain my treatment plan options and truly showed that she cares about my experience and my dental health. I highly recommend Enamel Dentistry and Dr. Rathmell on South Lamar for anyone looking for outstanding dental care.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3rBNXo5R8PRdmhZAAb1GwVjAgl3xmS2VUNjBoSGA_fpN_oEtlkx6pZkicMBXU2vsp8ofXtskc4AxfU3agT8J7XZHV1_WbgBubD4pydMtBh3fIt9SVhNNXzEPA4mPtFmV5jN8K3a8Azzdc=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-4"},{"Name":"Lauri Crowe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9FH0IhFsKFM9h09H9C1kV7818igd6EqMdp2ivNk3BFd2hfkM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing team! Great service! Dr. Rathmell got me in and out very fast and efficient. She is an excellent dentist. The receptionist Dani was very thorough and welcoming. Wendy the assistant made me feel so comfortable. Great experience! Highly recommend this dental office.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lianna T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIuWpBxQfvciGgk36Ix5DSqbocYYNrJG4L-celzCwk8ngBsUg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First and foremost, I am so appreciative of the front desk staff at Enamel Dentistry South Lamar, especially Danielle! Navigating insurance, making appointments, and all else can be a hassle, at best or a nightmare, at worst. Danielle goes above and beyond to follow-up, schedule, and just be absolutely lovely throughout. Thank you!!  I have had a great experience with Dr. Amante. It can be difficult to find a good dentist - and Dr. Amante has earned my trust. He is clear, professional, and does not try to oversell any procedures. I have also had great experiences with all of the hygienists at Enamel. They are thorough, kind, and professional.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chris","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJT_jQD_z2yC6I9vueOB7fUz9gJ01nP05bf2wTnD3j__2y0mg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an excellent experience with Dr. Rathmell and her assistant Alan. They took incredible care of me from start to finish. Both were friendly, professional, and very attentive. They explained every part of the procedure clearly and made sure I was comfortable the entire time. The injections were gentle and completely pain free, and I was in and out quickly. The result is perfect with a great bite and beautiful, precise work. It was truly a warm, comfortable, and positive experience with an amazing team. I highly recommend Dr. Rathmell to anyone looking for exceptional dental care.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Joe R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLw47RGJxDq5EqhoY8VO7LdH0YI3_TLs1R75ABkJbwGwNr7xQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great first experience at Enamel Dentistry on South Lamar. Dr. Rathmell carefully analyzed the condition of my dental health and immediately created a clear plan to treat my current dental concerns. I really appreciated how thorough and informative she was throughout the visit and I look forward to working with her as she improves my smile and overall dental health.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lauren Henderson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL_oKgDKCQfyDD8GSlq-KHtN54T7UqURY3ySH_GvJMG99OQ3Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I forgot to fill out my initial patient forms so had to fill them out upon arrival which set back my appt by about 15min. I knew I had a meeting and was afraid I was going to miss it due to the delay in starting. I expressed this to the team and even though it was my fault, every single person was so respectful and considerate in making sure I got out in time to make my meeting. Not only that, but everyone was so nice and knowledgeable in their position in that everything was explained thoroughly to me and they took extra care to make sure all of my concerns were addressed. I am someone who doesn’t particularly enjoy the dentist, but this experience was incredibly reassuring that I made the right choice coming here. Thank you to the whole team for such a smooth and positive visit!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ragen Brotherson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLMiKD9qhVOPQfCsnXWVigGsC7b2KLfqg4qmKYjQGT3N5dErQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place deserves its raving reviews! They were so nice and fit me in last minute, I was a new patient and everything was explained clearly. My teeth feel clean and I even got a free electric toothbrush! The dentist no longer feels like a hassle but an excuse to leave work early!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amanda Aymes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKPbUlH5l9sygcRsTzbNpiGG7eCqxmo3onuAh2XR9piLtfkGt0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"New to Austin and after a not-so-great experience elsewhere, I was honestly a little nervous trying a new dentist — but this place completely changed that. The office was spotless, the staff was professional and welcoming, and best of all, I never once felt pressured or upsold.\n\nThe deep cleaning was chef’s kiss — my mouth has never felt this clean. Everything was clearly explained, efficient, and stress-free (which is saying a lot for a dentist visit). So glad I found my go-to dental office in Austin!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
