","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Saqib Khan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKiYRHrRVYzDuxIupB2NKeejM6-K3SnsK6lZ1tsyZEaveVd-g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Stopped by here for information on a dental procedure. The front desk ladies were amazingg and very welcoming. They answered all of my questions and were super helpful. I look forward to doing more business with peak dental. This place is awesome!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Adrian Williams","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLpWM5H5LJj64oiqYe4Jx91mkH_czrNHNZZCipR4khs6AOMrfM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"They're not too gentle here with patients. Pulled a whole tooth with wreckless abandonment and sent me about my way no pain meds, nothing. Im not heavy on the medication stuff but I would at least had liked to be provided the option if need be. Pretty painful procedure and they only made it worse. Almost feel as if they were taking it personal and trying to teach me a lesson. Highly WOULD NOT recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rob Figueroa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW8tQYOGDVGXxSuNAzqu1lCxTT94pg7ZDQ6lPKhFAwHrwa77BdHgA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Be careful with Peak Dental!\n\nThis is a rudderless business with have no management and therefore no communication.\n\nDr. Luis Oraca and Dr. Zizi who first saw me have since vanished and left their clients to deal with their mess.\n\nKeisha the office manager for the north location who promised to help track someone down for us to at least get our money back has also decided to take the same direction and told us there was nothing they could do nor would she put us in contact with anyone.\n\nI have been passed around the over 2 years with my Invisalign treatment and have made no attempt to resolve the issue.\n\nI've been taken for more than 12,000 dollars by this dental chain and I have nothing to show for except lost time and a refusal to do anything about it.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Katherine Hill","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWkz3CUVHd4Tbrcw-4B5V4OsntQxxh3YqibMRmDXlgcwXveIi-8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As soon as I walked in the door the vibes were immaculate. Each person I interacted with was so sincere and kind. The music was ideal. They were upfront about everything they were doing and if anything might cost extra. Communication was clear and direct and they answered all my questions. The booking was easy. We didn’t have to wait at all and they were very thorough in their cleaning. I’m shocked because I often have pain at the dentist and even when they were flossing under my permanent retainer everything was so comfortable.\nI felt so taken care of.\nAlso the mouth guard was half the price of the many places i have gotten quotes from.\nTop tier customer service experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"AK Aliu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLkVEVXRCtvb6lcucQ0SN_A1Hg959Ui2pe6xDb_aRXu12cMXA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"1 Star — A Disastrous Experience\nI’ve been a patient at this location for over a year and a half, but after today, I’m done. I scheduled a cleaning weeks ago, confirmed my new Humana Gold Plus insurance over the phone, and was assured everything was fine. I arrived early for my 10:30 AM appointment, only to be met by the business manager — a rude, sarcastic woman who scolded me for being “too early” and refused to check me in until 10:35.\n\nWhen I returned, she rejected my insurance and wouldn’t even listen when I tried to explain that the office had already confirmed acceptance. Her attitude was condescending and unprofessional. The office wasn’t busy, so there was no excuse for her hostility.\n\nThis was the most unpleasant dental office experience I’ve ever had. I quietly walked out rather than argue, but I’m making sure others are warned. Peak Dental needs serious retraining for their front desk and management. Patients deserve respect — not ridicule.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Niraj","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKWO_xvsOHbMcTBLQ2sJc6G3Lg2uczcapUSNgYPbx_wVsdrfg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Chi Ho is the best dentist that I have ever known. He is knowledgeable, personable and efficient. He knows what he is doing. He placed a crown on my implant and applied several fillings in my mouth, no complaints.\n\nHe recommended re-doing another crown that another dentist elsewhere had not done correctly, he explained the problems that he saw, I am going to get that done soon.\n\nDo not go to any other dentist besides Dr. Chi Ho.\n\nThe hygienist, I believe her name is Keisha but I could be wrong, is very good too.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michael Burton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV5XCqx7mLUx1zBjdBbYPcJGOwF_j4QLyxTlQMbWxsC1aUmcekB=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Shady business. My wife and I were both given root canals here and we came to find out later that they were unnecessary procedures. They would say things like, \"we have to keep resubmitting to insurance so they will cover it—happens all the time.\" The reason they had to resubmit and pester insurance is because insurance did not view these procedures as needed, because they weren't. Not to mention these root canals were terrible and I even had to go to an endodontist for them to fix the work. This was all found out by us after having the procedures done.\n\nI didn't realize there is not strict governance over dental practices. This place will tell you that you need 10 fillings while another reputable dentist will say, \"let's watch these one spot over here and take care of this one cavity.\" They can apparently just do procedures and then bother insurance until they cover them, while hiding that whole process from clients. I am certain that most of the work they say is needed would be deemed unnecessary by another dentist.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nhien Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL9n9f_hqXZqnSQtX_tr3IFee9aABo_FVKdiMLULY6Jw54awA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Who's the receptionist at this place? Never got a call/text response back and LAST MINUTE canceled my appointment 2 times consecutively + my fiancé's paid invisalin monthly check up. I previously gave this place a 5 star, but this is slowly showing why it got a 2.8 star rating on Yelp. Please do better!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
