Whiz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjULB-FxJQk2GZpKDq7G4bKtgIL5gTZ2kssChW2VTZvGSb8A4nBz=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Shetty and her team at Dental Smiles are fantastic. They are by far the best dentist office I’ve used in 42 years living in Austin. Everyone from the front desk to the hygienists, techs, and Dr Shetty are kind, considerate, and highly competent. I can’t recommend them enough.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tanya Tarr","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocID_nN6YORIMNPW4R6YJjHcuVG872P-CB8HFqkHOId_JWEYWgM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I wrote a review 7 years ago but I need to write another one. I adore the dental professionals at Dental Smiles - Gina, Britney, Brenda and Natalie (to name a few) - everyone at this office is kind, caring, REALLY SMART, and deeply compassionate. Dr. Shetty is an outstanding dentist and I am very grateful for their help in maintaining my dental health. HIGHLY RECOMMEND THEM.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Y C (Lc)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXDWL-Mb787tXDScLcmfZ6fU0B4oI7POxbtBF8ewqYxZXx8RULE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been with dental smiles for 4 years now and I have no intention to switch! I’ve had a few different hygienists thru the years, all of them are friendly, knowledgeable and do a great job cleaning my teeth.\nI’ve also done fillings at this clinic happy with the work as well. And Dr Shetty is awesome!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Victoria Lima De Carvalho","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKYoHX23gr15tiBm4fP3mBPrZfxOQv0ISJMwACui_pljAvhUg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"TL;DR: Amazing team, comfortable experience, fair pricing. Make your appointment.\n\nI’m sure there are a lot of folks as nervous about going to the dentist as I was, since it had been way over due.\nThe whole team here makes you feel welcome and at ease.\nUrsula was my hygienist, and she made sure I was comfortable, and took a lot of care to make sure I wasn’t feeling pain during my exams.\nDr.Ana explains everything in detail, and is kind and reassuring. I immediately booked my procedures, and am actually looking forward to getting my teeth worked on, and back in great condition. Pricing for my type of procedure seems to be quite fair as well.\nPro tip: Get your cleanings 2x per year folks. Don't skip them…","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Courtney Fuqua","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLPefGvRz-kNUwhE_xOCKRWdVRYe9BYuUH2ajAX6Y_UIdTFUQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The staff the care they provide at Dental Smiles is the absolute best! Dr. Shetty is so knowledgeable and you can tell she truly cares about her patients. Gina is an incredible hygenist, her attitude and chairside manner really help me to feel at ease, even though I’m at the dentist! Thank y’all for providing such excellent care and service!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nefertitti Jackmon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVYQCLJHxHFXfFVBXWGEfuceLUfDCYz-rrfd2eUXX02rGvb6aTa=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My experience every single time is so positive. The staff are caring, attentive and very detailed. The energy of the team is positive. They don’t oversell anything, but provide good recommendations that I am finally starting to follow. Most importantly, Dr. Shetty was very careful to get my dental work just right, even if it meant an extra visit, as opposed to forcing a procedure to work when things weren’t fitting quite right.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Carmin Spells","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXA3y028u-zyMIbqs8d-hrUO6_fQ9MTTElO99Mio1wbhSqURcVS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love this place and the ladies who work here. I moved, however will continue to travel here for my appointments because