pointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Checks","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Free street parking","enabled":true},{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Laura Qyra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI_Xyq-W9NMyX1AlVkxax1Jnqotryv3z99x9kpMGH0N2q5ZVw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a dental cleaning at this location. The front desk was great! Also, Jessica was so careful and attentive, she explained to me everything in detail. The doctor that I saw was extremely kind and professional,  I could tell he genuinely cared about his patients! He also helped me find an Invisalign office for my orthodontic treatment! Definitely recommend this place!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"joyce Christian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKJVJ__buPvZVnKDpJItBIAJGvnBV4XBwCRfm4uorUJsdvIUpQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Everyone that I encountered at Avenue Dental was warm and welcoming. I get very anxious about going to the dentist, and they were reassuring and empathetic and made me comfortable. My overall experience was very positive. Special thanks to Dr Wong, Jessica and Diana ( I think that’s her name) and a shout out to Anna at the front desk who patiently and kindly helped me to sort out my insurance coverage.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Janet Butler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJLw8V8iSqBbD_P9deiU3Dqv5UUxn502SBxIqaSS29qwbUUPg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr Wong and her staff are great,\nEasy to work with.  In my case we are saving all the teeth I have left\nDr Wong makes sure you’re comfortable and in no pain\nThey work hard to get your insurance to pay what they should.\nIf you need a good person for a dentist she is the one","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jonathan Bouwhuis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXc_nc9-4Ynwj8xO4Mg3qDAFwJkvgNMIHim9L1ZR0ebKJ_l26Ym=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Wong is great. She’s thorough, gentle, and explains everything clearly. The office runs smoothly, appointments are on time, and everyone is friendly. She also makes great conversation and creates a really comfortable environment. Highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Christine Zhang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJE0iq2PXDgjHIas4mI8j8CMQhSWWylgMtrQ-e1LvS908L5TQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Have been seeing Dr Wong for many years. Always happy with the service. Dr Wong is professional, nice and patient. Very friendly assistant and office staff as well. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Regent Prince","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUIqBrWdmMusCsa4gjZLXuyzUskmNsdQ7reN2QbilbS1ifiFfo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great dental cleaning appointment!  From the front desk to the hygienist, everyone is always so welcoming. Dr. Wong was thorough and gentle, and everything was completed quickly and efficiently. Highly recommend for your regular dental care!\"","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cynthia Barbarito","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXcFFgvLMe8Lcad-3ZAw05w33GlRRQcVLp7K-xIu4Ez__GdREY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Writing a negative review is not something I take lightly, but I felt so strongly about being mistreated that I don’t want this to happen to anyone else. My husband and I have been patients at Avenue Dental (south) for years, and we were shocked to be denied my fully covered annual cleaning simply because I chose not to proceed with a deep cleaning, which Dr. Wong recommended during an earlier visit. I decided that I would think about it for maybe next year, since it wasn’t covered by insurance, and that I would still like to receive my general cleaning for the time being. This was refused. Basically, my routine cleaning was being withheld unless I agreed to an expensive upsell.\n\nI called my insurance provider, who confirmed: “Any member on a dental plan has the right to choose the services they wish to have rendered. The provider cannot refuse to complete any services of the member’s choosing.”\n\nWe’ve requested our recent X-rays and will be finding a new dentist come the new year. Meanwhile, I’ve paid my insurance all year and  never received the minimum full mouth cleaning. Very disappointing.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"younghee kim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ7AUqG9CGy3sLGxFBoe1UT5du7fXNVnrccN_KiVsCYp_oT4Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Doctor Wong has been our family dentist for many years. We love her and her staff.\nShe’s very good, prompt and kind. Absolutely no complaints. Younghee","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
