definitely be returning and highly recommend Toothbar to anyone looking for exceptional dental care.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0vsc3mGg3krhecJmIKb_pbCR_SSoM921oM3rO2ey6qF0CRBikJdHCoouR6NgZvDd9JxUfF3PKplMiENeo9WBBmvyydosJ78_-vlvcTWIHpLjGIJN1kP3K3XYpSJ-iVayrGkN0M=k-no"],"When":"2025-4-24"},{"Name":"Dana Arnold","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXRi17C13QukbNgmT0xyp5QZ_p0o7ItCE0wEpMkPesBbK1XvYs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My teeth have never been this clean before!! Seriously this was the most thorough cleaning I’ve ever had. Ally was my hygienist and she was so helpful and communicative and DETAILED. Dr. Gibbons was also super patience with my questions and talked through everything I was interested in having done to my teeth! Really grateful. I can’t recommend enough! \u0026 can’t fail to mention how gorgeous the office is.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gordon Buie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ_KPj9ZOd8GlN8PFWyBd0p3Ol6xQjoQleu1XhzKUjmghln=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I will strongly recommend Toothbar to family and friends seeking dental care.  The crisp contemporary interior design of the facility sets the stage for the well-coordinated and efficient teamwork of the staff.  Dr. Jacobsen clearly outlined the plan for treatment and readily answered the few questions I had.  Over the course of the procedure, she monitored and made adjustments to minimize any discomfort.  All went exactly as outlined. All these factors, from reception to treatment to checkout, combine to result in exceptional dental care.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Al Leffler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWI9Dls6IfjtYe3bcM5pJh4IbvgywrOfd3Grm76XiCTp1p9HI6hEA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Visiting with Dr. Barclay and her team is always a pleasure. They are so confident and understand the most current and importan