icture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWdL9V1ItrUDupTjNnb1a33nQwztgXEFxlgq0CeMuNA6-gMQhwV=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I highly recommend Glint Dental Studio in Austin! Everything at the clinic is top-notch - from the modern equipment to the warm, welcoming atmosphere. The staff is very friendly, attentive, and truly cares about patient comfort.\nThe lead dentist, Dr. Iana, is a dentist from Ukraine and an incredibly talented and professional doctor. I visited her for a general exam and cleaning, and the experience was excellent - very thorough, gentle, and stress-free. You can really feel her expertise and passion for what she does.\nDuring my appointment, I was also assisted by Fatima, her dental assistant, and I was very impressed with her professionalism, kindness, and attention to detail. Together they make a wonderful team and create a sense of trust and ease throughout the visit.\nThank you to the entire Glint Dental Studio team for such a great experience. I will definitely be coming back and highly recommend this clinic to anyone looking for high-quality dental care! 🦷✨","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Katie Wilkes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJTQwiojM3lisMjewxrFdjlJfqW8oCw7-5K66LN5QVhQeM33A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This was truly a 10/10, luxury experience. It was seamless from when I first made the appointment to when I walked out of the doors. The appointment was in-depth and efficient and I had all of my questions answered and we came up with a very reasonable treatment plan. Fatima, Diana, and Dr. Elledge were so kind and knowledgable. Couldn't recommend more!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Violett Gaida","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVOUBlfbgMehg0sPeld913Sy6JhmFXiuOm9bpOevLa84yPvlZ0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was looking for a good dental clinic in Austin and had a great experience at Glint. The space is calm, modern, and beautifully designed, and the team explained everything clearly without rushing. They did advanced scans that were completely painless and took a holistic approach, checking not just my teeth but also my jaw and alignment. The cleaning was very thorough and comfortable, and my teeth look noticeably brighter. Highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Desmond Jackson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK5dN2RacrQ9yqtIayxkPGjdLv-42PApwgUamuiLxqTJfT7tA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love this place. Everyone professional, makes you feel comfortable even if you had a bad experience in the past. I would recommend Glint Dental Studio to everyone who needs dental work done. The facility is very clean and organized. Everyone there makes you feel important. Can't wait until my next visit, Thank you all for the great care.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amy Bermar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUJFLSX5N0LlkDVcnaYF0Ub7HAyADp2_IB_r18Igjw62HuuCHbHRw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was visiting Austin and needed an unexpected appointment — they called me back right away and fit me in the next day. Lovely office, super-modern, gracious staff and the dentist was very thorough. So while I didn’t need more treatment, I would definitely go back if I did.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bianca Garcia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVnXtK0tYJtzdw2pmIPoAAvfG2gROP8SFLEKLRK89cUwTNIoUP3=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Honestly, the best experience I’ve ever had in a dental office. Everyone is so kind, compassionate, and professional. I cannot say enough good things! I am very anxious in dental settings, and they treated me with so much respect and kindness. The office is aesthetically beautiful in addition to being staffed by incredibly knowledgeable professionals.10/10","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"El N.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWoaXHOyk3bH5Ea_FW52pJU-Z0Ew2R1QM4N92wb82gKI8M03EOeAg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great experience at Glint dental! The staff was friendly, the clinic was clean and modern, and Dr. Iana was professional and gentle. They explained everything clearly and made me feel comfortable. Excellent care and service, I’ll definitely be back","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0B73r2fIhQlbgCT7UndAal37vE_XBeS9nCUohGwqLCxPqsPR8tsciL_WSVGmdOsO4wQaFMjCKRZGrPyjjbuQ0sDLG3BmE58T6Ukd90eMWq9mcgwGnw8kFR144X4SO8cuP0TWVy=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2JUHkmX3hKOnfT4My3_KB6gt10RLLRW0vn3rUfqEFfvlP6N5aF8CCEYaoNGHrPaTsUWk4NbNVV5sPbn_CKfl0oUp7rAzBMe9wxtafV8fGiwOwnjHpCFvrVjjHrTjBFM7tld46nEQ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn38G8Nm_RC_G--pzEgsv9eNbqLPpxnN6yl1eemTmKixch5GmArsg9VgjFTyw4mUx6tODvVCx62eahuPglMi3If8LSDXyaUt5nelZfhUCpOKnYK1TtQ0M8PUrzJscBlwZxdqIyz4=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3XkrqROMm7WMHKScaXHUczkSMfkqpQvQA7vcZcIaau-DPzRpkLY6s9vs5bm538Gs-I7vzp9xp1Cl6IN2Ubcg5HjcCI0QiX75iF_-13UUCbrF2_9MqqtOYOza1y0ciKg-y6Ayktvg=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3YVdLUUUq5CQUjIPxNDh8YDOhj2xyHBSujpS0L_sSXK18IbzcDvhxBsgwq3ZM7wlW3JGJgIZ_ggO1Xc5BysFwDSa4TVMDHSpbY6Xwu8Js_7REPzQbLqkmR4RdsbJ1Gld2eEwA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn15Vq2UIVCErMffEcOL10DtUp5v-ixmManqmqxA01q3bKreGAcseZ68eeomjt5R-j_jcd24AaZ9O8dl0vQTT6pL4BqraIbmVuEiXc5u3YuaqHxIB3WU-B7GKSHfq5DTdItoZ161Gg=k-no"],"When":"2025-2-4"},{"Name":"Jacob Ehrlich","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIgE1wfW1vrwqkMyAK6Y68m_5qJ19NhaqgIZY4DWTr71mlRSA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Glint Dental Studio has been the best experience I’ve had with a dentist in Austin. I’ve been to a few other places over the years, but this one stands out. It’s high-end and comfortable without feeling over the top, and the best part is that it’s covered by my insurance.\n\nWhen you walk in, you’re greeted by Diana at the front desk. She sets the tone for the whole visit. She’s friendly and warm and actually takes the time to explain what’s covered by insurance, what’s not, and what your options are. She’s also helped me with scheduling and reminders and she brings this great energy that makes the whole space feel welcoming.\n\nI see Dr.Iana and she’s been amazing. I’ve had ongoing issues with my gums for a while and most dentists never really dug into what was going on. She took the time to actually look into it and explain everything in a way that made sense. I always feel like she’s really listening and not rushed and she answers every question I throw at her.\n\nI’ve also dealt with teeth grinding for years and finally decided to get a custom retainer. Fatima, the dental assistant, helped me through the whole process. She explained how everything works, what to expect, and how to take care of it. She’s patient and easy to talk to and made the whole experience way smoother than I expected.\n\nOverall, I’ve been blown away by Glint Dental Studio. The people, the energy, the quality of care, all of it. I’m definitely sticking with them for all my dental needs going forward. If you’re looking for a great dental studio, I can’t recommend them enough.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
