98-k-no"},{"title":"By owner","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAGYpak9vyZq10vimukeDuaf0oCqX49irkq5efiFflI7B649SKLWCtez9c-XmqpsVW9uLY1oL7mszAA8V9Fkuf7Yxe0nRDPhnLRunydTQni2upQCn92slz3KRPbBim6irdvhPrT-jw=w224-h298-k-no"},{"title":"Street View \u0026 360°","image":"https://streetviewpixels-pa.googleapis.com/v1/thumbnail?panoid=brLOKYgt-eifx75IRHka9g\u0026cb_client=maps_sv.tactile.gps\u0026w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=85.445724\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":[{"link":"https://schedule.jarvisanalytics.com/frame/swish-dental?location_id=3970\u0026rwg_token=AFd1xnEnb45ewBFns6J-5p9AWZZTxkvJXowwdbJfEmMf2zkOFV_jC_9rkk574DU_QdsbneyS4S3ymvcIH30YEejtrL4IsHYr0GThIXpbyiD694OF1GjG8-s%3D","source":"jarvisanalytics.com"}],"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"102414865262926252463","name":"Swish Dental South (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102414865262926252463"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Dawson","street":"3715 S 1st St suite b","city":"Austin","postal_code":"78704","state":"Texas","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"from_the_business","name":"From the business","options":[{"name":"Identifies as women-owned","enabled":true}]},{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Onsite services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Cosmetic dentistry","enabled":true},{"name":"Emergency services","enabled":true},{"name":"Pediatric care","enabled":true},{"name":"Sedation dentistry","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Gender-neutral restroom","enabled":true},{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"crowd","name":"Crowd","options":[{"name":"LGBTQ+ friendly","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Hank Day","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU8LOxL9UrMuhuj_NQbwsXHndpj7yA6feykgQ_g9YVzQF2SD_I=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very nice experience. Something I can’t say about my previous dentist. They have state of the art equipment and the staff are great. The dentist was thorough and explained all options. The dental hygienist was excellent. She did an excellent job on cleaning and help me understand what I needed to do to keep my teeth and gums healthy. I would recommend Swish to anyone.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Christiana Scheibmeir","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJi-uRyHgnZtQ0M9UW1VFH6h9DVhyRrB5MsGFIQxsDBlr58yA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing experience at Swish Dental! I had a wisdom tooth extracted, and Amanda was absolutely fantastic. She did an incredibly fast, smooth, and pleasant job. I was honestly shocked at how easy it felt! The entire team was so kind, accommodating, and transparent throughout the whole process. Couldn’t recommend them more!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mandy Marino","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLIvr1TSfa1TmUaLUrF9Uabcn62HmGXIel8QszHNkhMF_v38g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My experience was really great. Check in went smoothly, and both Dr. Marx and hygienist were understanding and supportive of my nerves around going to the dentist. They answered all my questions and got me quickly scheduled for a follow up.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Morgan Belcher","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLZc9X5JGFxgGavCL5cZxOlMjli2iWME_tl5QpZLDplpgwirA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Staff is friendly but definitely not like a normal dentist I’ve ever dealt with.\n\nCame for my normal cleaning and apparently only had time for X-rays. I ended up having to come back two days later for my cleaning, and was told I’d have to have a follow up visit to fix my bite even though it was supposed to be done during the first visit.\n\nNeither of those two visits did any of the dentist see me. Just the person dealing with X-rays and scans during the first visit and the hygienist the second visit. Nobody went over my X-rays or scans with me either.\n\nDon’t recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jett Elliott","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIWnPWUEn7N73xrASnPJXQ3WIbPW4cHV5E7gMBFSbK4w9YI3w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Thank God for Dr. Marx. She just did my root canal and I can say without a doubt I've never had a better dentist. Her and her assistant are a wonderful team. So pleased. Big recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lily Cook","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK4L1f2s6OqAcJ-4075LNR5aWcvPn_8NFh2GJg7-Y3Jmfx-Ew=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a toothache that made me go home early from work on Thursday, and I was able to make an appointment here at Swish for Friday morning. I wasn’t sure how it would go, as I have out of state insurance, and this was my first time going to a dentist in Austin. Patricia greeted me a few minutes before my appointment and walked me to the exam room where she explained the process for new patients, including quick x-rays in the exam room, a panoramic X-ray down the hall, and a cool 3D Itero scan I had never heard of before! The whole process took about 2 hours from start to finish. This sounds long but it was efficient and thorough, my two favorite things. Patricia was kind and friendly and we had nice conversation while she cleaned my teeth before the Doctor came in for my exam. Every team member I interacted with, from Patricia as my hygienist, to Nelly who helped with the Itero scan, everyone was so friendly! The doctor came in and examined me after Patricia had finished the cleaning. She was able to suggest a night guard for my tooth pain, and even showed me the muscles in my head and neck that were contributing to my aches! I feel lucky and thankful that they didn’t try to perform any additional dental procedures when they identified that my ailments were muscular and not dental. I already booked my next cleaning and I am excited to be a new customer at this location.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Martha Lopez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIJsyGzh_jaMmSJ6lGI0bs3KkKsY7MSn7b8mI8D_GtyCw7O1A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"If I could give it negative stars, I would.  Took my nephew because he accidentally broke his tooth.  After consultation they gave us a price for a procedure, so I went and paid for it. He had to come back at a later time to get it done and after the procedure was done, he was told that he needed to complete the rest of the procedure at a later time and it was additional money.  This was never explained to us.  The representative tried to apologize for the \"miscommunication\" but there was deception, not miscommunication, on their part.  I asked all the right questions and made sure I was fully informed at the first visit.  They chose not to give me the full information and that is outright deception.  I will never go nor recommend Swish Dental.  Very sweet and nice people working there, but that does not change the experience of being outright deceived.  Neither does them trying to hush me with a free whitening treatment.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Maribel Snider","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJcbYKDGZs-ep0hLMGMZ2hUVm7yLQTWjEVpviLlTQVRHUCPCw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Another good dental experience at this site!  The office seems to have the latest in technology. Staff is very helpful, kind, and friendly.  Hygienist (Robbie) and Dentist were very patient with me as I asked questions.  I was well informed about methods and options for my situation.  I was even offered entertainment during my exam with a remote and a TV!   I felt like I was in competent hands my entire visit.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
