t cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true},{"name":"Paid parking lot","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Deborah Main","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWS32EGmgDxH-YPDsIUrG5IAqrxAufDad5ZYpVosuqQb3wNcSQ5=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Reddy and her entire staff were very professional, thorough, and kind. I felt well taken care of with excellent customer service. My experience was so great, I am going to stick with Dr. Reddy and not go back to my prior dentist. Looking forward to regular cleanings. Tina at front desk was super helpful too. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Autumn Duris","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW9KEfCff37DzldWxFgLkcmvDszGJypYsSfL_uiYgHvKeX6HhAhuw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had very high anxiety for my first appointment.  The staff \u0026 providers were very kind \u0026 empathetic to make sure I was comfortable throughout my visit. Everything was explained to me in great detail, I was provided with a very clear plan of treatment, as well as an immediate breakdown of expected out of pocket cost through the next 3 appointments. I cannot recommend this office enough. I'm so glad I was able to be seen by such a caring team. Thank you so much!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lawrence Humphrey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVr3e-3XLJWYWrfG-D2K-uKrx2HQv90XtQihDyrVUcA4H_xxAmfjw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I’ve been to this office twice. The first visit was very pleasant, with a friendly staff and a smooth appointment. The second visit was very different. I was offered a procedure that I assumed would be covered by insurance. It wasn’t, and instead of helping me work it out, the office sent the balance to collections.\n\nBefore the deadline, I called three separate times to try to resolve it. The third time, someone picked up to say everyone was out of office at 1:30p on a Thursday. By the time I finally spoke with someone from billing, I felt brushed off. Tina, in particular, was unsympathetic and unwilling to consider my perspective.\n\nIt is frustrating that a loyal, on-time payer would be treated this way over such a small amount. The clinical staff were kind during the appointment, but the billing and follow-up left me feeling misled and dismissed. I cannot recommend this office.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shane Smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIpgKf4DdoD54nL20qPpXseQ1LW2I2hEvzbpWv1ccO1PJYJpA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The woman at the front desk is highly capable and gracious. My dentist was very thorough and seemed knowledgeable. I am quite happy with my experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tarlan Eshghi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUVASbkGexBzxU3RTQztBM05ZUlAXFgKMPOTgRm4DyXqk0hSPKxrQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time visiting this office and I had a wonderful experience! Thank you to the doctor and her team for being so kind and thorough from start to end of the visit. I felt very heard by both the doctor and the hygienist, and I could tell they really cared about hearing my concerns to address them. My husband is a patient and had referred me, so I’m glad to have a new dentist in Austin. Highly recommend if you’re looking for an honest practice that will only tell you what you absolutely need. Thank you to front desk staff as well, she was exceptionally kind!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jayanth Reddy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXBNHt2O5_S3y0TSnf_M71I61V5ORoPMArqFM7SomN1qUMK3Xnj=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. D and her team are really amazing and very thorough through the entire process. I am so happy that my friend recommended a great Dental clinic.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bri Aus","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLor2c0M-FQkJ8Kv8cJ10mdHoH8fYl7iw0ph0o1KlytxG9l=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Thankful for the wonderful team at Midtown Dental Associates. They were very helpful in getting me scheduled quickly and their staff was amazing! Highly recommend this location!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brynnan Whaley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV_CeF3D2xbqwdvNeOCSkW69wnGL0h7nORa2qdnbabAXESwtW0c=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I began coming to Midtown Dental a couple years back when I got a promotion in the mail and have been going since. The technicians and dentist are first-class— wonderful, kind, gentle, and they never make me feel frightened or nervous. I especially love Tina at the front who once had to squeeze me in for an appointment when I accidentally showed up on the wrong day. Will always come here. 💓","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
