{"name":"Emergency services","enabled":true},{"name":"Pediatric care","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Gender-neutral restroom","enabled":true},{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"crowd","name":"Crowd","options":[{"name":"LGBTQ+ friendly","enabled":true},{"name":"Transgender safespace","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Checks","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking garage","enabled":true},{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"April McCreight","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVPrmJ8u4efGEdmEUt0NegK3W5Oi_zwoVSFbkUUJR5X2cUEKlw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The office is nicely appointed, with a cheerful, welcoming reception crew immediately greeting patients. The dental hygienist, Kaymen, escorted me with a warm smile to the back area, and promptly took X-rays and made me feel at ease. She summarized her dental tasks before starting the procedures \u0026 was very gentle and efficient. It was a pleasure to meet Dr. Martin, who made me feel welcome and well taken care of. I felt seen, heard, and respected. Am so glad and grateful to have found this nice group of people who know their business well!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ti Le","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJJBeQOKCm3Uw0EveyOpnalJZsFYez18IFjZYQfqdYR0rhYQQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been a long-time patient at this practice, and when Dr. Lindsey retired and Dr. Martin became the owner, I was happy to continue my care with him. I’ve always been able to get same-day appointments when needed, which speaks volumes about the level of care and service they provide.\n\nRecently, I had a dental emergency and was truly surprised when I was just expecting to leave a message through the emergency line, but Dr. Martin personally answered my call the evening before a holiday and went out of his way to see me and fix the issue the next day. On another occasion, when I was referred for a dental procedure, his office made my temporary dental appliance (flipper), but the delivery by FedEx was mishandled and not on time as originally expected. I moved my oral surgery up and  Dr. Martin personally stepped in to ensure it was delivered to my oral surgeon in time, so I wouldn’t have to go out in public missing my front tooth.\n\nDr. Martin is professional, friendly, and extremely knowledgeable, and I cannot recommend him highly enough. I’ve never had a dentist go so far out of their way for a patient. Exceptional care and customer service all around.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shelly Dullnig","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIRgB062awYFgcUOaB46ZqE7udxTt4huyc9w76sNoVNA9-DOQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is great! From the moment I walked in the door everybody was super sweet and made me feel comfortable! Darlene helped me at the front desk and even remembered who I was from setting my appointment! Yesi and Dr Maddox were great! They all took their time and answered all my questions! They’re reasonably priced and have a great financing program if needed!! If I could’ve given this place 10 stars I would! I will definitely be back!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Daniela Ariza","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKSSfhdRCKyJIU7zy-1g1Gs-V9LZcofA-Xb8G4f1sECtYiCU7Y=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I'm so happy that I found Balcones Dental! Everyone is very nice and very professional, as always. Their service and prices are great! I wish I could know everyone's name to add them in the review because everyone is so kind, welcoming, and very professional. They really care about people!\nThank you so much! ❤️","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dylan C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV8Vwm5ffOOvZuRpVGLECLxIUY5Fzgd5urdaZiTSiSHNKa2ulkL=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best experience I’ve ever had going to the dentist. Caymen, my dental hygienist was thorough, professional and friendly. Dr. Martin was as well and very empathetic even though I needed a treatment plan with plenty of work. I will not go anywhere else from here on out for my dental work. I’d give an extra star if I could.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jessica Blankenship","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWUR7Ba1J3yY4Yr9kkEW7JG3k1dEE1nlZT_tbfk_cm_laycf_I=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great experience with Dr. Martin and his staff! I'm usually pretty nervous at the dentist, however, the team at Balconies Dental were so friendly and made sure all of my needs were met! I will be recommending Dr. Martin to everyone.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vincent Torres","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLoceZpUYdqeuL3qUXiJnRHiGv-9YSXjWFGzDi0L9ONCPfg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had my cleaning today and Dr. Martin addressed a crown that was installed by a previous dentist. The cleaning, crown adjustment and night guard were handled promptly, pleasantly all during allocated cleaning time. I feel very positive about my teeth care with Balcones Dental and all their staff.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Melissa Liscano","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXORlV7jIC3hMUs2safv-YUQSKmNIwvpoTjNS0ERYDnbZZpifms=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Martin is my favorite dentist I’ve had. I tried a few practices in town, and I will be loyal to this one forever. I drive 25 minutes across town to get here because a good experience at the dentist is worth the trek. The whole team - from front desk to hygienists - is really kind and professional.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
