EHg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love Magnolia Family Dentistry and feel SO lucky to have found these women when my dentist of 40+ years retired. They're friendly, compassionate and funny, and extremely gifted in their areas of expertise. I recommend them to all of my friends and neighbors who are in need of dental services.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marci Davenport","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW9buRwrO0oyoPKocIUcl-dNiPD1bTI2k2SrmO4Ya-yqxdALk_m=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was referred to Magnolia by another medical professional that I see on a regular basis and couldn’t be more excited to have found them. Their team is wonderful and welcoming making sure the “dentist jitters” are minimal. The technology they use is newer than my previous dentist used which made it much nicer that having that expanding purple blob in my mouth for impressions:) and, my treatment plan was explained and broken down in steps helping me to make a decision that also worked with my budget. Very grateful for the referral!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1a1pAsZmxW6SnQ-TUdSiJzDjMzvD45ie1Y1zv_BtrEWMnXXlBJt2p1aJiux_eVtRgW5RXaxNoY0cxGiAwG03EpyNSk_ijJyYue2L98a0Afg8Oo08gW4Fx-MIXE0rJDc_QVNIOwl6EgLfE=k-no"],"When":"2025-7-3"},{"Name":"Dani DeLuna","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIf_ngJe1StUlRzPKyduyIctsUC3Ir_1tfhHWbWQtUbD5ROGg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This office is top notch! Dr Burton \u0026 her staff are professional \u0026 personable; the office is warm, private \u0026 so clean. An old fashioned practice with modern dental technology.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Joanna Farwell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKcKSvSNeVa1XuZv2pJfftqZwPWUg0qkWmPWYBQMirTiqzzaw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Burton and her team at Magnolia Family Dentistry treat their patients with utmost care, compassion, and patience. As a self-proclaimed dental-phobe, I hopped from 1 dentist to the next many times over the years and never found a dental practice nearly as supportive and caring as this one. They are competent and kind and do not try to sell you unnecessary treatments or products. I am empowered to make decisions over my dental care on my own time. There is no pressure, just facts and gentle reminders when I come in for a cleaning. Plus, the imaging technology they  are using is amazing. Thank you, Dr. Burton, Emily \u0026 all your staff for taking such great care of me!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Carson Craig","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUxugBGiRLjV37EXFHB_SiOcfGh5MJLc523dqy91aPce5O80k4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was overdue for a dental visit and was anxious about it, but everyone at Magnolia ensured that I had a wonderful experience. Everyone on staff was extremely friendly, knowledgeable and helpful and I look forward to seeing them again soon!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"edna alaniz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVcaLRqPkXns_1QJgAqsXWI3mrImee0kzEnNsoTRkRsiMa-TOR3=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Emily is such a joy to work with and always puts me at ease with her kind demeanor. I referred my boyfriend there as well and now we both get our teeth cleaned and cared for at Magnolia Family Dentistry! Convenient, fast, and friendly!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
