aring and competent.\nI’ve had dentists in the past who complained about the work I needed.\nDr Glennon recommend to me by a coworker. My first visit was a great experience I have  been receiving treatment since 2006.\nHere with Dr Glennon Jessica Judy Sarah and the rest of the staff I have had caring and informed treatment with great results.\nHighly recommend","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
