-/ALV-UjUQhX1B7ZbToN9aFsHAGa7dkdqlVaRZd2UFIE5w-ovisWLDSTo-=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Not like any dentist I have been to before. Dr. Trivedi is very knowledgeable, which is great in a dentist. But as I went on longer as a patient, his staff seemed to prioritize this new \"airway\" therapy over answering my dental questions. They tried to sell me an $100+ \"tongue therapy\" course to help me sleep better, without me mentioning any irritation in that area. I eventually left and went to High Point Dentistry, which has been better for me.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"J B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKUItSW61O37CLgzRAZoFIBDWWjwxVmTnDWOsI8UxWAFu3PLvQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This has been my dentist for years. I have always been overwhelmed with how kind and professional every experience has been. I would never consider leaving them for another dentist!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1WnFsJtdqjGpqz41vvJW6ZrnLtSTwpH4JvdA2P7x0ziop_D3EflCRl_nAZC-8rirOHfzwTyoysqxDCD71skJyJ4iZFBCaeEHN2-yeH3WUSiMiGIk2Uk2pIGXKpz5i5G8gyCYCIsIok_v0=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2zsNtuVs5d5C3SjPthAcNfTIIoUzywZ6A7KEaZKh_ZmY1e6kdaEJfwhgmWZAtVIqc5Jz2bTcjE1XHlL6Ez5NsWTgCiYxXGaPKGEHEDKhkz-OzA7lybNxAk2Oh1zP0wfk5CdyTKozHGokjF=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0iblsZUaBejO6ahn4zhy9ETwNEP2m7NcL0ypRJVLLLEOVwhGrF7Q3Cas_0ZHN1Urel-jnu-Ls7V5VQ3IxcgLgFRN8a9R6zoewLVrb4viRYUghvmuJWNToxD8nf2OR9HUo3OJrXyBHKZ72K=k-no"],"When":"2025-8-4"},{"Name":"Michael C.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXzsbOVctHAd_U5LJ_v92puHzlqQs0gQAVc84JWr9Av_O5stB0t=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I just finished up a 16 week myofunctional therapy program with Maria and have to say it’s bittersweet. While the exercises and frequency of visits took a lot of effort, it was an awesome experience and the benefits on my breathing, swallowing and even sleep have been life changing. Without exaggeration the CT scans showed a 190% improvement in my airway capacity.\n\nDr. Trivedi is awesome and thorough and offers a level of care that’s unique for dentists I’ve seen. Somewhat experimental in practice but as a student of life, I appreciate the curiosity. And I’ve learned a ton. I finally feel like I’m on a path to better quality of life/health. Highly recommend. Jessica and Maria are both wonderful humans and amazing at what they do. These folks are family now.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3ChwFHveXNDh2zQWlnxSlXZWJvUVjy9stP0FadFmnU111i2XsPeDQz2VrXK3SAEa2q5Dbr9HEToH8Wr9EgaqzWnfiNNxDmhtObrLBxrVxoBEYI8r-gZR5usx792XK_SB6Nqf8_=k-no"],"When":"2024-11-26"},{"Name":"Tammy Oatley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJMVRnuL718raY2MaX7beNhdFYw1nuAwMcb4MepZytX9tccTw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. T., his staff, and office dog (and CEO) Zoey are truly amazing! They have made me feel so cared for with every interaction. Dr. T.  takes a very solution oriented pragmatic approach and took extra care and time to give me the best smile possible. This is the only pain free dental work I have ever experienced - I actually almost fell asleep. I am so grateful to have found this office. 🙏","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2UQYVhDbkT0FPps7cU9QKglYgY9USkOrXtkPmZBUObFsqKDb3lSOl34XSxU-FX0X59HgCFzKtQ5O3zMF2vICOWLzmei8Tjd_Z2217WF5m0r5UrbrOqmnyZfsewKRWV6inda8XE=k-no"],"When":"2023-9-18"},{"Name":"Gennifer Castillo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWZoo0Ba10QIm-iZNvHHMYbH-sScWy35yEs3gJmWmz_a1cEMHOs-w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a great experience at this dental office! The entire staff is friendly, helpful, and welcoming. Dr. Trivedi is very knowledgeable and took the time to answer all of our questions thoroughly. We felt well cared for from start to finish. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lynn Bakes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJ7g5kdkOgpJ5GZBVwx7YhM4G0FhoiBRu-dM43BPL26_rmsyia=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was our first visit today and we had an excellent experience! Dr Trivedi was very knowledgable, answered all of our questions, and all of the other staff was super sweet and helpful! Zoey the dog was also very cute! We brought our overtired infant and they were all very sweet with him too. Would definitely recommend!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1-Ui8ZFns-QNP4FrmDBoOwvun92_NKADIDNFpG-RslaZs5PAuWLgIP8sQ-zpkcwSs-YY7H_kvDO4oSyPA6xxmLYJqbsh3v5LNYxumBN_-kTST_wEvKwGhLn4vfTDPO5vZ67zqDcQ=k-no"],"When":"2024-11-15"},{"Name":"Waynehedd","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV2LLEYIeow2ws8TrChRu2zGKKM28dWFm4xxN4hHE78BN7vUwJa=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I highly recommend this dentistry! Dr. Trivedi and his staff are incredibly professional, knowledgeable, friendly and helpful. I came here as a transfer patient from another city (for Ortho FX treatment) and everything went smoothly. They were able to adjust and help me with tight timelines and always made me feel comfortable. Dr. T is also really forward thinking, personable and an all around cool dude!... his staff and practice truly reflects this.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lexi Bohigian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbrOZUjbFCoZ1kw28NOOC6XguqcYmT1HhfCA-HKD9gCVLIbF_g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Not an actual dentist office anymore as they are no longer offering cleanings or regular dentist services, just trying to sell “airway specialist” services. I’ve been coming here twice a year for 8 years and really enjoyed being a patient,  but now need to find a new dentist as they cancelled my 6 month cleaning and are no longer offering cleanings until further notice.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
