5,"Description":"This is my second dentist visit this year because my first experience at another dentist was awful. I had a great experience with my annual cleaning here! Finally! They made sure you are well attended. My teeth were super clean after my appointment. I would recommend anyone to come to this dentist! Thank you so much","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Justin Mauldin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXqzEbPLbFUTRC5NdrCKudL5JZmlB0A-VmX-rGbUXdZaPSQ7nvz=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve had multiple procedures and never had any issues with the quality of work. Can’t say I love going to the dentist, but as far as they go I’m happy.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Megan Hicks","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWzZ6UzVjGFz9t6KjdA-6S56_GeqklyEOw2sGNws-xxGWBZ0ZU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an extremely positive experience today. The staff were so kind and helped me feel at ease. I was happy with the treatment plan the dentist came up with and am looking forward to going back. I recommend Rivery Dental for anyone needing a new dentist!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sam Lansky","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU4s8qO2_e3FsNQx7fExgpW4Hvdgr2tTUUtW7toDVakUO6BKrs-=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been going to Rivery for about three years now and always have been treated well. The team is very well educated and friendly. Michelle is a great hygienist as well and will leave your mouth feeling fresh after a cleaning","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Grace, Pin-Rong Wu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ430MlEyVwNXT4gtUsiT8ptAo_UtCEG4HCcm5TnvQZuw3NAQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I highly recommend Rivery Dental! Dr. Wang performed my crown treatment with such skill and care that I experienced no pain throughout the procedure. He was always thoughtful, checking in to 