92009"},"complete_address":{"borough":"East MLK","street":"4100 E 51st St Ste 100","city":"Austin","postal_code":"78723","state":"Texas","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Emergency services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Brett Collinson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXwA-tzhYSlAXJRagvq37w1UGpukqpft7_npaWJZNajROQn8YPF=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a fantastic first visit at Walton Family Dentistry. Dr. Danelle Walton and her team run such a professional and efficient practice, but what really stood out was how patient-focused it is. Everything was so thoughtfully done – they made sure I understood what was happening at every step and felt totally cared for. It’s such a refreshing change from other offices where you feel like just another transaction. Highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jonathan Norris-Green","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJIfaH0ytrGDFYYoCcjfGCw0hX8A2eWKIrLa4T_H1royuWVJw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love this place. Dr. Dinelle takes a whole body approach to dentistry and explains how dental health can affect your body systemically from heart health to inflammation. She is the reason I finally got to the right specialist to address my nasal obstruction and sleep apnea. I recommend Walton Family to everyone I know.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Estelle Paus","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXqk8dwGgIEW43XX5B26C7vWfM-9aTGDsDqn9yPMcreZsjfBkX1=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Walton Family Dentistry was my first dentist when I moved to Austin. Despite moving far out of the neighborhood over 2 years ago, I continued to make the drive, because they were kind and responsive.  This summer, I was informed via a text that my cleaning appointment was cancelled because I had to miss my previous periodontist appointment with another provider. I cancelled with weeks notice.  This was not a \"no show\" situation. I didn't want to, but it was necessary. And I figured life would go on as normal and I would get back on schedule with my dentist appointment going forward.. But the people who book the appointments at Walton Family Dentistry cancelled me with no notice and said I could not make an appointment because the periodontist would be contacting me to schedule an appointment there. They did not. I pleaded my case, to no avail. But I was met with absolute refusal to work with my situation in any way.  I was not even allowed to message Dr. Kyle to explain the situation. Just on principle I am not going back.  I think the dental care was fine.  But the office staff are just a little too impressed with themselves.  I am still incredulous over the experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"T West","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXWAjy8njQ1oIKmz4OtjLsv-7q9BNuKCXl5zC7lcx4OpreDplnP=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is how a dental practice should be - excellent by every metric.\n\nI do not like to visit the doctor, however, I am very discerning about who takes care of my teeth; and there is only one dentist I trust implicitly with my teeth - Dr. Walton.\n\nIn fact, I upgraded my insurance plan to see Dr. Walton...and is worth EVERY penny.\n\nExcellent and professional scheduling and reception.\n\nExcellent and professional dental hygienists.\n\nA sparkling clean, brand-new, bespoke clinic with the latest in dental technology.\n\nMost of all, there is Dr. Walton - to ensure my teeth remain in good health through communication, concern, empathy and patience.\n\nI will continue to visit as long as I am in the Austin area.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1CuSFv1G_0_SEn5dv9-p2RSyRAB-2eOHokMLlWz5n0L-g4YxVhDMG19HYsJ8-dBY0iv-a0YasdMpRplCwUr995b3BOrnslPHoiwYtNLT4FIzAyLslu6fjYgkK3hY7Kex-R3j8t=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn30raY1rxK8Liosv5xKwcY2GE13TgbjRaEXQQQZyO1IXoUf_bUDE6oPsju1Oi9XXAjgUEtAz9DkN6NGBgcwtNGuHMRAs2_Pw7T_yEdOeQQj3sFAkiopOEfTcd5fKtSQd3zsTKpHtQ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0U93NvqBKktV7f7c9DVkNb0K9_ombxtzb63H64xJuND-T1JPXiznFU4smCUqk_xOQWyjKp-wnmPfhfJQSoKrmWxi5NWUkYuYHVAJtmHJS1s_xc4uQgY9kzzTylHbm-ZN7HI7Ms=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1IlLnEmN05cyMXuAUFt_3cWhRZeJiHXv0rqbeHKQcoMPeQgYPNVxX9FdLnR58FtlpKkZKp8THLVAX8k_x9MjHU7GiAp3sDqWMmFUtICvcO1yuTgr9b3PlEaJki05otxwjE21FW=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0BVXaTEPxinKJEbp0wWLISHphmK_v2SFGyBVBrPsO0rapsgfYLusex2yNjH8qm3sYjVNavEuOMhVsJgt7MXJodbZzlXQbyhd2Z4ExwxXmguWtGYGBj5HVNbHYMs_NI-MRVzDU=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2RSI7KqRAhiHXKvkiTtwosAGloRb5_-uz1HmDtGgqHPJO4qieBlY2DRKJGNuVdjHS9Y7c0ij1CBD9pWm9l8NrwCdDU1f6AVYpGstPV5bd75nAH2lS61vN-YDfwCJF-2_25d_7Y-A=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0SOF41qIY0xJQHC6Y1vyo6WuHbURhZZCrm6zRXduWvbRS5zR_T6gZ8CUcfBEooih8GzIxTgzmJKNtWhW8N-egqjnj_zX9yVk5q3Awb8E_iHC6rlauB6ObpdfHrp0a-ogcTH8Xt=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1N2Z2mF2y4bM4Y1p_1PgjQ0BSui9z1TNSImP5Z-l_tUMfdVsH3hvFVnua1pBbM2TRf3Mdr7RzhLFTgo3N6vaTPYEtOV7mDfA8GDEetsSG96FqRWkeaAKxeSTXqMQ2g9tQZ9gCmIw=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0N2aB12UZ-mclxJh0_6Q_bWPNF4GVlPNpndYZJwFNRC8PkigPB9itYfmtlZAo-pTDk3B0D-DCJNsGWoYKe8AjAEJW9L_Kp6PsGlu7j91k0SwdVD1Y2SZlGpp92v7eFNeEdmrBa=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn32_5IkfP_XeNkeRHnqnRq3EaEkRXGB2uQSDzb3cNvLdvRfyHGwcwwg5Uh1S76hr_XDR-DLaBt3HhIQAv9DLrk9BE405FBu2mQc-RpwU7jHQwTW4PqZkV2I2lojQhRLnXVpGwYzPQ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1QlkuAfvky7btOLk5218NnkUjSXwHoy-1A7xHtT7EKn11DDnkEKLcZ7ncgJBXrR_MqJddh4pqQmv-F5F5MWvXVgvs3-IwKNdoyviZN_k6YWTEiYrlwl-yKHZX1sqD5uC-5z3yO=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0vFx5xJf7PDpArQAX88OgdDxGGsAbvFoORzOIMIx8qC_GI10O2iIb8DrTJ3arzPJSd6G1xbdr8jneTYQpbFFwt9ppqR0LPAQ2WfupS6XGo9i4dLmUaz-r23NRnMa9P0YFupxKQ=k-no"],"When":"2023-5-6"},{"Name":"Ethan Miller","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKoFjAzyqOIrEltKcZ9ZI2ECc9kgCWaCj6JNTvHBWBveIdQgQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Literally the best experience I have had with an dental office. The communication from the front desk, regarding scheduling and insurance was amazing. Everyone was very thorough with making sure I understood everything. Hygienist, assistant and Dr. Kyle were all amazing. Again, great communication through out the entire process and you can tell they enjoy working for the company.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tiek Johnson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNz-rV2Nf2j1GUh6YGg8u_YiRyQWRjbTh73cxl4yUEN-D34oMV=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I had a pretty poor office experience at this dentist. When I scheduled my appointment I was communicative that the time was close to my previous obligation and that there was a chance that I will be late. I was assured that that would be fine when I scheduled the appointment. It was indeed not fine, and I was charged a cancellation fee, although I was present for my appointment.\n\nTo make matters worse, I was told that because I'm a newer client, I would not be extended the grace that they would extend to an established client.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kay Ice","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJN50EhKPVR6ciVU5VB1pggdr5S6MI1RQx7ccjadNp3th5jfQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve seen both Dr. Kyle Walton and Dr. Danelle Walton and can’t say enough good things about them as well as their practice. The hygienists and assistants are all wonderful and really care about their patients. I wish I could give ten stars!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Miranda Molen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW5n2WzENoAw5IkQd0TzB0s1Xfm8ADY5AgJzY-5ybW4TbHA1p27=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been coming to Walton Family Dentistry for years, but for some reason I have never written a review, though I’ve recommended them to many friends and neighbors over the years. If you’re like me, then going to the dentist is anxiety inducing. But from the moment you walk in the doors, you are put at ease here. The front desk personnel is always friendly and welcoming. The hygienists are always thorough and knowledgeable. Today my hygienist remembered a conversation we had 2 years ago, which is pretty remarkable service considering how many patients they see in a year! And both dentists, Kyle and Danelle are incredibly kind and gentle. I have never felt like they are recommending work I don’t actually need. And when I do need work that requires Novocain (aaahhh!), Kyle delivers the most pain free shots I have ever had. And this is coming from someone who had fillings in my baby teeth, so I have had a lot of work done over my lifetime! Finally, the personnel who handle the most painful news of all, the ones who take payment at the end, are always very thorough and knowledgeable as well and ensure I’m clear on the costs I’ll be paying for treatment and am comfortable with them before booking the next appointment. I cannot recommend this practice enough. If you are nervous about going to the dentist, then this is where you need to go!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
