g","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Victoria Herrera","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLhNnvCr3hL7rExzIC7A_y-MIRjI1ksVF1uYsNysVq51ADxgw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"10/10 in all ways!\nFrom the consultation, Kelly made great suggestions and had a listening ear on what i wanted and what I wanted to prevent. Carmen is absolutely delightful and welcoming.\n\nI was extremely afraid of dentists. I have always had abrasive and uncomfortable experiences, but Dr. Patel and Ms. Julie made me feel comfortable and heard. I’ve never been excited to go back for a dentist visit except to see this pair.\n\nDr Patel is a perfectionist who takes his craft seriously, and it shows with his attention to detail. The experience, work, and bedside manner is worth every single penny. I’m incredibly grateful to have stumbled upon them when I was researching cosmetic dentists. Thanks to the team!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jessica Taveras","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK74Ee7b2AxyO96J4Txh8l8UDM5LlIbB60Xa6-8x1G7OVmOiw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hi all,\nI’m just here to hopefully get my question answered by those who have had the experience of getting their porcelain veneers done by Dr. Patel. I really want to get my smile done by Dr. Patel I can tell he does phenomenal work, but are we really talking about $30,000-39,000 price range for veneers?, and at that not even a full mouth just the amount of teeth you show when you smile. That’s way too of an exaggerated price, I mean might as well get a down payment for a house instead.\n\nCan someone please share the price they paid, I’m just trying to clarify on pricing.\n\nThank you! 🫂","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Katie Corcoran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI8jzRj6XHvC0PDPW9yO4BqSrXsmq5kJVmC35FKD0w9TUu7lnL9=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I can’t say enough great things about the team at Dr. Patel’s office. First of all, everyone there is incredibly friendly and made my husband and I feel like family. Dr. Patel and his assistants are incredibly detail oriented and spent every minute needed to make sure we had the smiles of our dreams. The whole process to get veneers was much easier than I had assumed and we had new smiles within a month or so. They listened to our thoughts and opinions and edited our temporary veneers until they were absolute perfection. I’ve followed instagram accounts of dentists in other countries for veneers for years and I can’t express how glad I am that we went to ACD. I’ve never seen before and afters like the ones on their page….absolute perfection. One million percent will refer anyone we know here. Thank you guys for being so wonderful and welcoming and making the process to amazing smiles as easy as possible \u003c3 - Steve \u0026 Katlyn C.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1TefclniPPRCTntUpXT2CVNUiYrPK_HcPygj864i4WmWGx8KW46zvScHT7RiyuD_3mWhruPMV9ZfNO_6lSoF9FEl8btsCQ9GYmqEqo89bQDFAJVlRf7eEwPwwPxcoc8-2e31-NQg=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3XNUUCLCf3se02QC5yzV8MS0vI0T5b6Nylq0B1oShGWp03-7w5d6Waoa_fMjJAAwndwn3VAdjZ5245KcSZuaxrFK2WNHJ30DSvqp0q-EaA2O-zze7iFpMGAkx9T2wuCgvgFxFS=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0lJKx3EcbOkx0cn9_OaiPydXf4xUD3mptJ1_OYdJci_s8oW4P4GoCgaZlsBLW2ydhri_ARBqil-TTJtFdmWzH55RKpe5fwY19MNRtZWPYU4lyyvuoFtkz39N-gD7jjN7ZHpgpS=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1eWjsAYbnHDzkJ8xJsd7dHFSHcHi-DpnVGsneVTuAhfyk6SLfsP_tpbVUsDv2zxvdQhM0JQwqoODmN7QbWNA2qPFYmCnqZjzuUwgIItpQEYZkCx0UQvVtTXb_6WjCntsTvTHnE=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1ppvaJVIIq2sOh_vT3l10G45xYuVdTjthfd2Nvu6wNWIVK0-moel4gd82APjcle4EqotyFvbEq61kaP2aXN-8rw6G_IHUN8EtWwZS5zoiLGF3Hc4kNG2x49qjFLYILK114f52C-A=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1baEwpvK5YnvIgwFkCZ7Yf6bBwMPjTuCPhrRH25nBJg0PJdG4HqPgFfC2_5FQ8bfIl-gSy5hE1X8khXSuM6f9vlR61U_LXuYO7xUTN428rmlSVNCdNuAWeQNHA_rL9oQyDo0o3=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1b6peZy4Xqx8DIPb0gxROlRnBYR2ozxAbyQTGiXOLUcvlGLTCZSHCql96Xp7NcnOu_CSs6POb729M2GmVnEVq7bM0E9mDWRqb2LKihjDRnML8rieiZTln_B3U6TQfA_lBeYbpA5g=k-no"],"When":"2024-7-17"},{"Name":"Firas Hannawi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJfhOGRTIKPx3D3FvUBDnMg9EpP6Bh4TtaYF7e6Tv9Mj2hGZg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently had the pleasure of receiving dental work from Dr. Tejas Patel, who specializes in veneers, and I couldn't be more thrilled with the results. From the initial consultation to the final placement, Dr. Patel demonstrated exceptional expertise and a keen eye for detail. The veneers are flawlessly crafted and have transformed my smile beyond my expectations. The process was seamless, with Dr. Patel meticulously ensuring that each veneer was perfectly aligned and matched my natural teeth.\n\nNot only did Dr. Patel deliver outstanding cosmetic results, but the overall experience was also remarkably comfortable and reassuring. The staff was professional and friendly, creating a welcoming environment that eased any apprehensions I had. Dr. Patel took the time to explain each step of the procedure, and their dedication to patient satisfaction was evident throughout. I highly recommend Dr. Patel to anyone considering veneers—my smile has never looked better, and the confidence boost has been incredible.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn301aYhxiY04fEP1LmWwLEGiIShilOz4VZj_YxZtGrxHUqUETEXV76QtjsweCkbDsRpCZ9OkCVNsZg5P3a5vpNKFwuPB6byPbtt7TMpl1d2lCMg2Cncw8kt7G50HupKTSqU5FwI=k-no"],"When":"2024-9-4"},{"Name":"Tony \u0026 Liz McD","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU0vjU3XxUgYYD-o5snJvOT6UJx67EIZNUF3ixdP6LRVYSKcVqt=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"100% would recommend Dr. Tejas Patel and team! My only regret is that I didn’t do this sooner. I did 4 separate consults and Dr. Patel was very honest with me in his suggestions and recommendations. He definitely was not the cheapest but he was the one that felt just right for me!\n\nFrom initial consultation online to veneer day, the communication and overall process was superb!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0gk0IARDaiiSqHx6yODUy9QEEjU3rWmJSfVcVbBVBi1B374qCNTO0mZAMnGvYx3qFdTBZ0Z3OlIn68HzFx0_Gd64Bgh8pQ1QYdO2EyvEAF6lp6s7iW2Ts-nhZ9NqXEO3QdHC_dmwxpNK0=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn14cUQ4cUNNGldmvEyHvlVBS_-N1MY6sNDYMmlV2MwlL7tlbgKR1Q5lAsPfdpN-FBcSPGotFZLrFPQJ0wtaanPXbiPhvhia1K3A65VRoBq_1i9einG8SspKW1rSZDOBagYq25Pf2BlzFvy-=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-11"},{"Name":"Kayla Hale","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKSlxD75yMnVJZRdLsVtiX1UUxBbYs2gze-d5adn-aJnD1DJg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Patel and his entire team is superb. I had the best experience! I was from out of state and they made the process simple and easy for me. Besides this- I am in love with my new smile! My teeth are perfect, I love my new shape and color! If you are from out of state I highly encourage you to set up a consult, you don’t regret it! I interviewed 2 cosmetic dentist and chose Dr. Patel and I would do it all over again.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn31SLwjEK4J7I-Zr8LW-XCMqkccbnPZ3gtP038uYbct5pm4_DdBuW40PxuW4bUb3qxa0XwVyJBCRQ8R_THZ7I7Q_a-P-LykFv2ahmXss3NWRjas00E-KIHVP1GWpY4frfdDMib5eQ=k-no"],"When":"2023-9-27"},{"Name":"melanie little","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUZ51KBB052iBKs4hDRqeGbyvMssWY7AjGeDy0vAdJlfMFltDY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"From the first call to the day you get your veneers the staff and Doctor Patel make you feel like family. The offices are bright and inviting.  This was the easiest experience ever!   I’m super happy with my “smile makeover!”  My teeth finally show in pictures and look bright and white.  I love the size as well!  Thank you to all the staff and Doctor Patel for a beautiful confidence builder!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Allison Reiss","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXf8jeDu7VcVRmEfN7En_wg5olr0Xs1ecomJkCsUhzDqFrmjlKCiA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I cannot say enough wonderful things about Dr. Tejas Patel and his incredible team! From the moment I walked into the office, I was greeted with warmth and professionalism. Kelly, Carmen and Julie are beyond welcoming—they truly go above and beyond to make you feel comfortable and cared for every step of the way.\n\nDr. Patel takes a consultative approach that immediately put me at ease. He was incredibly thorough in explaining the entire process, answering all my questions, and ensuring I felt confident in every decision. His attention to detail and expertise were evident from the start, and I knew I was in the best hands.\n\nThe entire experience was seamless, and I felt genuinely cared for throughout. And now, I can’t stop smiling—I absolutely LOVE my veneers! They look natural, feel amazing, and have completely transformed my confidence.\n\nIf you’re considering cosmetic dentistry, look no further than Dr. Patel and his team. Their skill, care, and dedication to patient happiness are unmatched. I highly recommend them!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
