26thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"116095276627988680523","name":"McLane Family Dental (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/116095276627988680523"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Brodie Lane","street":"5000 W Slaughter Ln Suite 200","city":"Austin","postal_code":"78749","state":"Texas","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Cosmetic dentistry","enabled":true},{"name":"Sedation dentistry","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Kathleen Cap","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKYyPMvQGSE-sXElK4wND4nl9sR5uZFGL3JUIo52A1aadsQJQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Genuinely good people who care about their patients and do all they can to make the experience comfortable and easy.\n\nWhen I moved to Austin, I was not looking forward to getting a new dentist as I’d only ever gone to the same dentist in my hometown for 20 years and that place was unbeatable I thought. I tried another dentist in Austin first and they wanted me to fix 5 supposed cavities I managed to get between seeing my home dentist and them within 6 months. Felt immediately like a cash grab so I came to McLane on recommendation of some coworkers and sure enough, no cavities to fix. McLane does not play the upselling games or mess around with your dental health. Just friendly honest people I’ve had the pleasure of going to for the past few years.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jessica Escobar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU6yL8PPUVHKyZHNWPk37HcYZ6dhYy8eXNi6AnTwIVQ126DEKbK=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a fantastic experience here! The doctor and the hygienists spent a lot of time explaining what they do, why they do it, and how they can help--incredibly thorough. I dread going to the dentist because I don't want the awkward sales pitch of what they're going to upsell and having to say no. Dr. James and his staff didn't do any of that. We talked about what was best for me and he conservatively made those recommendations with my health in mind. They make you comfortable with tv, blankets, even aromatherapy! If you're hesitant to visit the dentist, come here. I am so happy I made the time to pop in.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mary Bock","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXlxYWFMZNCvvnIp8rTNjBDmuqPSho72hoFS6kWm3d78K1A0jh-=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been with McLane Family Dental for ten years.  Everyone here is caring and competent.  They keep to schedule, something I appreciate a lot (appointments start on time!) and the hygienists are top-notch.  I no longer live near the practice, but I'm such a fan I make the trip for my visits.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rebecca Blaine Carton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUExUwUqtngEPET4ZWs9zECWvYHW9TchjNYFqI9Rb6Sl-g031_rtQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was a new patient and they fit me in really quickly. The offices are nice, the staff is great and Dr Deidra took time and care to look at my teeth and provide thorough insight and advice.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alii Katt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUUQqudEQzxHBE_UfB66d6mpJhsU2rAcVHYdx1gJ814cHmlsArrNQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have had great experiences every time I have been here, all the staff are very warm and friendly. They also do their best to accommodate you and keep you comfortable. I generally have a lot of anxiety around going to the dentist but they always do their best to make it quick and painless for me!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Anuva Bonzek","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWG5Qz7d0LVupALUPVrLzKASXR0X9lDbuiIkpq9ZIWjt9kfAgWucg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr Deidra is the best! She is always very gentle, kind, and thorough in her explanations. The staff and assistants are also top notch. In addition, the warm blanket and choice of TV show makes it a definite 5 star experience!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ina Jensen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK6tHgd-PSrEvBUEGxWWkkmf6A44iz0Vt5jShfeksqcCOtWMw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This dental practice gave me the mist complete dental exam I have ever had…. Inspection of gums, teeth, crowns. The dentists, hygienists, office staff are friendly and knowledgeable and can answer all questions about procedures and insurance.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"khushbu agarwal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX6evzzuSEBgJjqZlC4CoL1yeG2vDM17RJxl07bCUEEpCCmJMDvOw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"great front staff, and amazing hygienists and doctors. They are so thorough every time and genuinely care for you to have good oral health , without pushing any unnecessary procedures","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
