ts","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true},{"name":"Paid parking lot","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Galit Stein","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJOMO_1X-qJIdsAHhaXf12qPPveCiBaRTF1Uz9YxDXsJRgxMQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I just got a cleaning at Bridgeview Dental and feel great! I’ve been going here for 4 years now and I’m always happy to refer and recommend this place. What a great team! Xtine is the front desk receptionist who is friendly and helpful! And Joanna always does a great job with my teeth and gets rid of any tar I have. 5/5!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alexander Saal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV4hW7ZxizokichsD66Ln1_wwswprO1heWVYTGuhd2BsIoNhfzy=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been going to Bridgeview Dental for a long time now, and I couldn't be happier with the care I receive. From the moment I walk in, the staff makes me feel welcome and comfortable. They're always professional, thorough, and take the time to answer any questions I have.\n\nWhat really stands out is how they consistently go above and beyond to ensure I'm well taken care of. Whether it's a routine cleaning or addressing a concern, I always feel like I'm in good hands. The entire team clearly takes pride in their work and genuinely cares about their patients.\n\nI highly recommend Bridgeview Dental to anyone looking for a reliable, quality dentist. They've earned my trust over the years, and I'm confident they'll take great care of you too!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lori Patterson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV1JPvkEDbB1LGY2_t0cSEC2Xjzu9choor1V0j4qhbTiWdCYL2tWw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am so thankful I found Bridgeview Dental! I just had two crowns and two veneers done and I’m elated with the results. Dr. Loveless is honest, down to earth, knowledgeable, and professional and helped me renew my smile to my exact liking. I really appreciate his team and the state of the art technology that his practice offers. I would highly recommend Bridgeview Dental for cosmetic and all other dental services!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Zac Castro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVTeoAttwUMsiOCXJZ30B_6MGSyM7Q6hVX89AvYSZBzZumPPC96Yg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Professional and welcoming atmosphere. The Bridgeview team has nothing, but great to me over the years. The dental work and care has always been excellent. Bridgeview treats you like family.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"KDC","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJzeYzS_dlNFcnM2ZEklWTgaZQrmQRycecgdfqsd8LbT5PZ-Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was impressed.  They were very flexible, kind, and straightforward.  Usually being at a dental office makes me very anxious, but I was comfortable here.  They did not try to scare me or hard sell me.  The prices they quoted me seemed pretty reasonable relative to other offices I've visited, and they were transparent.  Paulina did my x-rays and she was great.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kristen Driscoll","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUXwKxobTWJJY6mHwf8o2pEbXrbTh9ugWAghPYedcW5LKOMFOQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I originally came to Bridgeview on a Groupon for a discounted cleaning. I had been burned before by dentists who tried to upsell me services, so to say I was skeptical is an understatement. But these guys are EXCELLENT. Joanne did such an amazing job on my first cleaning. I did need scaling done and just returned last week for that service. Again, I was blown away by the incredibly thorough job she did. My teeth look great, and I’m confident she helped stave off some the horrible side effects that come from untreated gum disease. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Maica Jordan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLQromxHwKVfKSmh9TdWzzOjE0UI-0afIFloWtYecSAZR8PnA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Dr Loveless is wonderful - makes you feel welcome and safe and informed. Appreciate his team too - they are kind and professional.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Annette Galloway","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIdA1n07W4EP7E6CK7s8_uZJtj1lVDqSmpYoiY279nBtw4P4g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Have you ever had an appointment, walked in and immediately thought ...Dang, I'm in the wrong place and honestly I felt I was in the wrong place just by driving to that particular area.\n\nWell, being an African American Black Woman, it happens often and it's not always a welcomed and friendly experience. ( I know, even in this day and time- it still happens unfortunately).\n\nI would like to say Thank you to Dr. Loveless and his awesome staff for not making me feel anything less than the millionaires or even thousandaires that walk thru the door, KNOWING I was not qualified financially  to afford his beautiful work. (I should of realize that by looking at his picture gallery).  There's not too many of \"me\" in there displaying their smiles...lol\n\nDr. Loveless called me back to the office to consult with me and I think he realized quickly that I was actually poor and had a State job w/ State insurance that they don't accept at his location for the services I needed.   Dr. Loveless continued to consult with me despite- showing me some images and displays of what I might consider, explained a lot of information, as well as what to expect going forward and what I needed to do. I thanked him sincerely and apologized for wasting his time- he immediately corrected me and assured me it was not a waste of his time and I wasn't in the wrong place, as his assistant gently rubbed my back comforting me because she saw the tears wale up and knew I was saddened and want my teeth pretty and healthy again.\n\nSo- if you're in need of dental restoration and getting your smile back to give away, please consider \u0026 call Dr. Loveless, where the name could easily be Dr. Love\"more\" because that's exactly what him and his assistant gave me that day.   If I'm ever able to save for my implants, it will be with Dr. Loveless and I will be the first one in that picture gallery!!\n\nAll my life I have been complimented and told that I have a beautiful smile and I just want to be able to give it away again to make a difference in someone else day.  I work a lot and see hundreds of people everyday of my life.  I love to smile.  I can't let  these ugly teeth take that away from me. I won't give up.\n\nThank you Dr. Loveless","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
