icture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKWFy2j_fZDHyr1TcuykQynvj6q9MgY3dEV5op9qKIrPs-2mQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Kristi has always been so receptive and accommodating to me (I’ve rescheduled a few times). I really appreciate that kind of hospitality and service.\nQuinn is the hygienist that worked on my teeth and she is great at casual conversation and has a great bedside manner. Makes the cleaning experience easy and enjoyable (as dental work goes).","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Larry Ryden","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLHMF93OMmZ_CuiUJhE5VVGaiXOSweGv2-agDaAv3PRfVX49g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Madere, Christi and Quinn did a great job with my 6 month teeth cleaning appointment.  Everyone was on time, professional and made me feel like everyone appreciates me and my wife as a long time patient!\n\nLarry R","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bart Hudson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK7YdZuL21mNyiAU4zIZumvO5WkrofnDO1WxR0jYCSyQf3frg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wonderful, Friendly, kind and very good at what they do. My family and I have a dentist for life.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sandy Halbert","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLRoiUa13FG05T8ooAOAHW_uErvt6gL2t4USCTQQ_m-g2BXMg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Right from the front desk with Christi to Sara awesome staff is amazing!! Dr Madere is the best! Always explains about the procedure and what is  going to do. Very kind and caring!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jenn Bailey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW2pdUY72mgCeeOWQA1PHhfLL0GrntKUbXIWlcnd0KvJTboueEbbA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nick and his team at Choice Dental are the absolute best! I haven't been to a dentist in 15 years and I have super sensitive teeth, they took great care of me so I was comfortable, not in pain and everyone was so kind and helpful! My teeth look amazing!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Edward Alpern","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV85-TcDTm0u5xek8m2YYJHwIvDuZgBzCynUD-ZtfRTu1z24ns=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Even as a long time patient, I was nervous going in today, facing a procedure I had never had before. The exam was thorough and Quinn and Dr Madere put me at ease about it. Quinn has a light touch and the whole procedure was pain free.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"tiffany pham","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXdz8ZPLMx5sXtUr-cC6RnBB-gtteqzbX7-IwWIHyWqMjwOeo8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I hadn’t been to the dentist in over ten years due to negative experiences as a child. Unfortunately, time caught up with me and I found myself in need of some root canals that were causing a lot of discomfort. I came across Choice Dental after reading a forum that recommended them for patients who feel uneasy about dental work and I’m so glad I gave them a try.\n\nFrom the moment I walked in, the experience has been nothing short of excellent. Sarah, Christi, and Dr. Madere were knowledgeable, friendly, and incredibly accommodating. They explained everything clearly, made sure I was comfortable throughout each visit, and truly changed how I feel about going to the dentist.\n\nIf you’ve been putting off dental work due to fear or anxiety, I highly recommend Choice Dental. They’ve earned my trust, and I’m grateful for the care I’ve received.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
