:"LGBTQ+ friendly","enabled":true},{"name":"Transgender safespace","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Shahidah H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKhkvb1dDNPLq5M_wARRRaUXsDNrYH8H2TkYT1kIBz4mVecCg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had to have a tooth pulled and was referred to see an oral specialist, but I found Emergency Dentist of Austin instead — and I’m so glad I did. I was able to get a same-day appointment, which was such a relief.\n\nFrom the first phone call, Amber gave me so much helpful information and made me feel completely at ease before I even scheduled. Dr. Smitherman and Savannah were phenomenal — kind, transparent, and thorough. They went over all my options and even asked questions other dentists never asked. That really stood out to me.\n\nThe extraction was quick and smooth, and they completely took away my fear of extractions. Both receptionists were incredibly sweet and welcoming as well.\n\nIf you’re nervous about dental work, this is the place to go. They truly care about their patients, and it shows. I truly appreciate each and every one of you ❤️❤️❤️❤️","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0FqC-wNw--iVSAeg8b2P4N2FIerb0L0vhkxkRpYrw-3avdDF0m4M0KImRFjeagMMArRwJzgkFu0lNPv01782NAjGGj7m4-UdTTiFqH2FiA0e50SJRYwbujgvfgTKVaHzEdae6XuwBPa8Y=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-21"},{"Name":"Freya Hilinski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXOfhgxEf14vo88wqVqVcjP7gekDRHyaGxQIvkDuBBEI27oIKk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had to come in for a possible infection, and the staff were great! Amber took awesome care of me, and made sure I understood the procedures and what would go into them, as well as how to navigate my insurance. Very grateful they’re open on weekends as well so I’m not having to take as much time off of work.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0DcMTkqc48W5NxdV6ibCcyWX5TRDyletgWNHlEEM0lXp5IUrNc4rsQl1B0B-x5n9I1Cd598l4gyfx0uc450OAyOSNE6zgNDnRLZjKsuJOrHbneGmqyPdKm9AXnf7VrNVV0ZlQAl_2w1V7d=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-14"},{"Name":"Kayla Rae","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWFwJGkSKE8VVDOtVybQE8q1K_Xf52zzJSYowUGlwIjJeznbshB=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Here for an emergency extraction, everything has been smooth and staff straight to the point. Luckily found the right emergency dentist to get same day work. Amber and Dr. Dudeen have been very helpful. Will use this clinic for emergency services going forward.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1eIDmzwDXpBPwF683SBiliAqVZBrYtkQ7lIET_6YYoQRZzHcTY01RLpVY8quxg1XF2ob9G86a3JJainU3955IbjZzIS7j5xUNymKdFpKFlIsHuJZ4Z2yDoQcxGNL_TK5BLNYQQqEvjT9d_=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-20"},{"Name":"Steven Mufalli","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJBg3lIE7Joz3cyys22_9K_as_MWh7a_phGj-njHm84DnPCnQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I entered in so much pain I could barely think, because of this my blood pressure was soaring, and I was feeling extremely frustrated. This crew went out of their way to make me feel comfortable and relaxed, until I was ready for my extraction. Everything went quick and smoothly, and I appreciated all their patience with me during my visit. Dr. Smitheran was excellent, Amber and Maggie were so helpful in making me feel calm and relaxed, and the manager Raouf was extremely kind and understanding with his pricing to help meet my needs in this emergency situation.","