e":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Barbie Chavez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWnwdNYHvq1sTCAl_vv9lMSb5oGh0ot_Y_zFbaQ4orTJff-eAM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My first visit to Swish Dental was nothing short of exceptional! From the warm welcome at the front desk to the skilled care provided by Dental Assistant Bernice, to the Hygienist Selena, and Dr. Nguyen.  Every member of the team was courteous, friendly, professional, and genuinely committed to patient satisfaction. The appointment was punctual, and each step of the process was clearly explained. I'm thrilled to have found such a trustworthy and outstanding dental practice. Swish Dental has truly earned my loyalty, and I highly recommend them to anyone seeking top-notch dental care.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Parsa Kosari","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVe2yeyo6GbHHGElr7j0nrbt9JZGl48m6pPiQZxniAK8Sifv-R0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I don't think I've ever left a bad review for a business. But my experience with Swish definitely requires one. I saw them in July of 2024 for a cleaning in which they told me I need 2 more cleanings in the same year. I listened to the professionals and came back. 12 months later, they tell me I OWE $700 and my insurance denied my claims. They waited a full year to tell me, instead of telling me before I ever had my first, second, or third appointment.\n\nI want to work with healthcare practices that are honest and forthright with their work and practices. I think the medical staff of Swish Brodie was good, but the faults of the remaining staff really ruin the place. I'll be recommending everyone I know to AVOID going to Swish Dental for as long as they're around.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Wilmer Berrio","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXNOPcAGDsQBERIt2jo7K9WN8J97nCb1K9eo_LsZ049lhBNv0oYVg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The overall experience was terrible! I started my treatment very excited because everything was clear and I wanted to see results. The dental service itself was good, but they kept changing the payment terms, adding extra charges that weren't discussed on the first day. You're now obligated to pay to finish the treatment and see results, so there's no seriousness or certainty about what was agreed upon at the beginning.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Olga Olinka","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKLo_32VyXSYhyp6cOH9g1HY-fFa5o0w9kSlTRVgEWJYIzN3w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Appointment was very comprehensive.   Staff made me feel very  comfortable.   I liked Dr. Nguyen...he was to the point and explained my x-rays and my treatment plan.  All in all great visit...and I am fearful of dentals...","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Eric Shuff","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKoa3IaYzMV0uPzP9yIha-nQNLeMBKg6rXM8a32ZU-gAWR5QQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I think the doctors and the dental work from the staff is fantastic.  They are knowledgeable and do great work when you are in the building.  The logistics of the staff in charge of scheduling and managing clients/insurance is abysmal and is enough for me to tell others to stay clear.  Communication and lack of empathy for patient’s is the reason for the poor review.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Melissa Rojo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJExARt_uK9dDcN6rUIPfNeNBPttPUqwzp84Ac1BbZX_L-OZA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My initial visit included the detailed comprehensive oral exam/cleaning (Selena)  followed by the exam by Dr. Nguyen.  Selena was very thorough and gentle even with my large tori which makes it challenging when doing X-rays.  Dr. Nguyen was personable in his exam and his overall demeanor when discussing his assessment.  Office staff were very friendly.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kayla Rosanno","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV4GIbhVqYXydVSei-VDtIRWPBY9LupIJf1bDDa_N4dUF3iBw8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I have been a patient for several years, primarily due to the convenient booking process, broad insurance acceptance, and accessible location. While my visits have always felt somewhat impersonal, my most recent appointment was particularly disappointing due to the terrible customer service I received from the support team. I left feeling undervalued (truly like just another number) and that my experience as a patient was not a priority.\n\nTo be clear, the front office staff gave zero F’s.\n\nThis visit was the tipping point and encouragement that I needed to find a new provider.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jie Huang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKqc49OjRsJL01UdBmXfANiZ1iwBa9tFJuWjFI4ZlN_m6MuDQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Clayton Nguyen is the best and very attentive. He takes good care of his patients and I can tell that he always has our best interests. This location wouldn’t be the same without Dr. Nguyen.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
