d taken from their families yet you turn the way a potential customer at a business that you don't own and sacrificing the dentist money approval point to your ego. And  my HMO insurance He rode me from Round Rock to Austin They also feed me on the 1st of every month and I also have no coffee or co-payments no payments for prescriptions so if you thought you was embarrassing me he wasn't and I know exactly how to find a dentist too bad your dentist missed out that you for 😏 It's important how y'all dentist professional know who's at your front desk Because they behavior takes money out your pocket and food out your kids mouth.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kristin Scott","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLJs0Lwhdz3Y1ap1PiP7YoWYAx0jCaZWnXeBSrwSTG27FPTqA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am one of the many people that fear the dentist, and I had put off going for like 3 or 4 years. Dr. R and her assistant Cindy helped me, and they were truly the nicest dentist/hygienist I have ever seen. Cindy really prioritized making me comfortable, and Dr. R treated me with kindness and compassion. She explained everything really well and without judgement. I literally never write reviews, but they did such a great job that I felt like I had to. No more anxiety over going!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kelsey Radican","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU0K9I2OdFJN2yyqmNLCs4aYcP61R3Ktfy_Z-zmdSxLU79v8sxv8A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had my first appointment here yesterday and it was a wonderful experience! The team was so professional and kind and took the time to walk me through each portion of my treatment. I am so happy I found this dentist office and will be recommending it to my friends and family!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Teresa Harkins","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJSYkFC7FL3uEzJpvWw2ey87ZnzxugSDcrhOht8dBKAkGZYuw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100",