smetic Dentist of Austin has been wonderful. I’ve been wanting veneers for at least 5 years and decided to  go for it. The process was very seamless and I was well taken care of. A huge shout out to all the staff. Everyone always had a smile on their faces and made the environment very welcoming. Special thanks to Dr. Barras for making my smile beautiful. If you’re looking into getting veneers, I can’t think of a better team of professionals than the group at this office.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"A. M. Lozano","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI-tBQcChRXykCBKlaTAjBv-bBrSTJMRhHnC1IYT1ewh-qP2us=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I highly recommend this cosmetic dentistry  practice. Everyone I had any contact with was so welcoming and professional. Their expertise was what led me to use them. As a medical professional myself I truly recognize and appreciate the outstanding level of care provided by the Cosmetic Dentists of Austin. The team led by Dr Hay, utilizes state of the art techniques and technology which resulted in a truly remarkable and precise cosmetic outcome. This practice sets the bar for quality and patient experience in the field.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dalia Rodriguez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJcpb6Hu0zHsef2ZQgBgN8GT6sAIwcwKEpn1HxcWhnNKQRXjQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is the second time that I get veneers with Dr Shiro and his staff. I absolutely loved my first set and knew that I wanted the same results. If you are looking to improve your smile and confidence,  don’t hesitate. Before my smile makeover I always felt self conscious, but now I love to smile. The whole process is very personal. At no point did I feel uncomfortable. They listened to what I wanted and exceeded my expectations. The whole staff is very friendly and very professional. I couldn’t be happier with the results.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null