MG4tmKEjMwy0sYM2R1pHZBj5ucWagkWyKaF6yQxU6qjzeSVBWQ0VU=w298-h298-k-no"},{"title":"Street View \u0026 360°","image":"https://streetviewpixels-pa.googleapis.com/v1/thumbnail?panoid=fJtSe9tJ3iaTy9AQnN6mIQ\u0026cb_client=maps_sv.tactile.gps\u0026w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=61.536728\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":[{"link":"https://www.smile360atx.com/consultation?y_source=1_ODIzNTM1NC03MTUtbG9jYXRpb24ucmVzZXJ2YXRpb25fdXJs","source":"smile360atx.com"}],"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"112223978124573472295","name":"Smile 360 (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112223978124573472295"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Zilker","street":"1509 S Lamar Blvd #675","city":"Austin","postal_code":"78704","state":"Texas","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Onsite services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible seating","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Gender-neutral restroom","enabled":true},{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"crowd","name":"Crowd","options":[{"name":"LGBTQ+ friendly","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Stephanie Dockrey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjViMv6fyHtV5Rzse9lFeod4rSJ9eW4v-RvKkfA0h_0ksj9hAo8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been a patient here for several years, and every visit has been an incredibly positive experience. From the front desk staff to the dental hygienists and Dr. Ip, everyone is consistently friendly, professional, and welcoming.\n\nI’m especially thankful for the care they provided when I chipped a molar during my pregnancy. It was a stressful situation, but they took the time to explain everything clearly and made the entire process feel calm and manageable.\n\nI also really appreciate their holistic approach to dental care. They do a great job explaining how oral health connects to overall wellness, including sleep and they emphasize preventative care. They thoroughly explain all options, including Invisalign, without ever pressuring you and they make sure you feel informed and confident in your decisions.\n\nThis is a kind, knowledgeable, and professional dental practice and easily one of the best dentist experiences I’ve ever had. I would highly recommend them to anyone.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tiffany Joiner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJSxysOpZKUhElMTYIC7DGIAKMsj0fy8ToxejIljVZJwD1kUA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am sincerely grateful for Dr. Ip’s exceptional care. He has assisted my entire family with airway concerns, including our one-week-old daughter. Dr. Ip performed a tongue and lip tie release, which immediately improved breastfeeding. Additionally, he has helped my husband manage his sleep apnea through the introduction of the Vivos appliance, and he has also provided Invisalign treatment to straighten my teeth. Dr. Ip and his assistant, Shae, are highly skilled and dedicated professionals. From the moment you arrive, Lindy makes you feel welcomed and valued. I highly recommend Smile360 and would trust no one else with my family’s dental and airway health.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn15_BMj7KbNo31-O8JgRmATZO6N3a7bBH4sQc9Bk-GzarYtTLLn9pnqAGIufqm7yeZUvFuvtUpRnR-7X3FXub0uf6gou_SJoN1BvEQfQkYpQjPd0cWuZxN1GlMmD854lk9Bjl5-3Q=k-no"],"When":"2025-4-24"},{"Name":"Erin Ellis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9sQdKV6_wl2dGFJWGwV_hoNCE3blL75JCDUFJsL6_JqKAnyAu=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Ip and his team are the best in town. My family has been with Smile 360 since 2018 and we're never leaving. The care is excellent and every single person that works in that practice is warm, friendly, and knowledgable. Dr. Ip is extremely thorough and loves to take the time to explain what's going on with your teeth and gums. He and his staff are also amazing with little kids; we recommend Smile 360 to everyone we know.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shannon Cedillo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIVMkFF1T0Msa0k4E968vV0yLjCI4Vg3Pxe7iP1q9MOz1ZyfA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I started seeing Dr. Ip in 2017 with severe dental anxiety, and I couldn’t have found a better team. Dr. Ip always takes time to explain everything clearly and makes sure I’m comfortable with each step of my treatment. Lindy and Erin are wonderful, too — kind, patient, and genuinely caring. I fully trust this office with my dental care and actually look forward to my visits now!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nitin Raju","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwyPQC8N3Jpshx2-z2fP8oXpSUq8Sf2CDdu7_KP71zAQfAtRtc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been going to Dr. Ip for about 7 years now and wanted to thank him and his staff for the wonderful job they do. Dr. Ip loves dentistry and wants to make sure he provides excellent care to all of his patients. He is always furthering his knowledge by attending all the cutting edge lectures and uses high quality materials at his office. See you in 6 months.\n\nAs a disclaimer, I am in oral surgeon in Austin and have worked at Smile 360 in the past. However, this is the only Google review I've written for a dental office and I do keep coming back to his office for care.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2eu7FksH8mWpj5NcqMlHh4BK4cMJm7gpXlcRKsgMmq8GF6FORhMwdC6eM0nsiFi37DhU9Fh1V4kuSAFrxBd3XiNoL2qty9WYC0qXyQoXhyMv9gUTetlIqmh64mBq7QOU1z3KkM=k-no"],"When":"2024-5-9"},{"Name":"Paul G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUThC6ojp5hhWlIU7F--qHofeRpGzwIcxDAGyIDTnojRL2e8pY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Outstanding experience. 12 months of aligners, and I'm extremely happy with the result. Moreover, Dr Ip and the staff are the most professional, friendly and accommodating folks I've ever dealt with -- can't recommend them enough.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"John","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGS-hCf1lOVGm91f7w0OH_wcMckg5JqfR1QcEFHKoMOYFWFG4s=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"My doctor sent over a referral several weeks ago and nobody has called me to set up an appointment. I have called their office on two separate occasions and nobody answered the phones. I left voicemails with my name, contact info, and asking for a call back so we could set up an appointment but still, nothing. Their service might be great but I'll never know because they refuse to contact me for some reason 🤷🏽","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Casey-Jane Weinstein","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLnFY5RvGHRdksdEsM9qObfk4zERUTHLPUNXG7hcg3MweavsA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an amazing experience at Smile360 with Dr. Ip! This was the most detailed and comprehensive dental appointment I’ve ever had. Dr. Ip took the time to explain everything clearly, making sure I felt comfortable throughout. The cleaning was quick (and painless) yet thorough, and the entire staff was welcoming and professional. I left feeling confident about my dental health and well cared for. Highly recommend this office for anyone looking for top-notch dental care!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
