ointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Niyah McKinnon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIi5VZBAt0p4TM9QFiKre4qOhfUJLegp0aNwbqxUj-8hZ1J8g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great customer service. Dr. Ngyo i believe is how you spell her name, helped me feel reassured at a time when I was going through alot and was nervous for the whole experience. Dr. Hijazi is efficient and also caring in his own way. Going to the dentist makes me nervous in general but I have had great/lifechanging experiences so far and honestly just grateful for care and attention to detail.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gina C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocID9uh_ulDGNfycm3KP32YCtI0Pdg8Nwdfk6iLrLNTcCayeAw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Maxey is great \u0026 Dr. Im is amazing! Both helped ensure an unfortunate situation turned into a reasonable resolution, ever so thankful for both of their attentiveness, professionalism, and care during a difficult time. Have been to a number of dentist, none backed their work or ensured their dedication like these two. Book here, you will not be disappointed ‼️‼️","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marisa Menchaca","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUOaEyvhLBLF84ese-47XgI0HSH8IDgEFMvE83TYd9ex4MZ-gpkoQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been going to River Rock Dental, in Mueller, for almost 10 years. I have always had wonderful experiences with my cleanings. If there is ever work that needs to be done it is always communicated and you are given several options for treatment. I moved to Leander few years ago but continue to travel to North Austin just to continue my services here!","Images":nu