026cb_client=maps_sv.tactile.gps\u0026w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=82.64568\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"116093534526957398947","name":"Austin City Dental (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/116093534526957398947"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Rosedale","street":"1500 W 38th St #37","city":"Austin","postal_code":"78731","state":"Texas","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Emergency services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"crowd","name":"Crowd","options":[{"name":"LGBTQ+ friendly","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Free street parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Carter Pearson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUikjREvzKUbA6C2kBHjSXjwLxBWkYDUJvLs1J0Q0Fzx9GjgEzj=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is hands down the best dentist office ever.  The front desk staff are incredibly friendly, responsive, thorough--you can always reach them and get a question answered or appoint changed without hassle.  Dr. Cook and all of his dental professionals (hygienist, Invisalign experts, etc.) are friendly, knowledgeable, punctual and professional\n\nThis office is a well-oiled machine, the entire staff takes pride in getting you in and out promptly--I have never waited more than a a few moments to be taken back or seen by Dr. Cook/the hygienist. It's clear the entire time really values their patient's time to the highest degree","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Judy Carter","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ-qDOe6KL4ZtuahWQ3GHQvhyHabqpSZKti947BBKqqfnevZg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My first visit to Dr Cook and it was a pleasure. The office staff and the doctor made me feel extremely comfortable (I am a very nervous patient because of an incident in my childhood). I am normally anxious about going to the dentist in general, but today I had none of that anxiety because of the excellent care and attention by this office. I would strongly recommend Dr Cook to anyone interested in a new dentist!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Greg","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVfAEyCQ0oIW_Ukl7keqjTCpC_jevG3PrgQcQHwgGAYk3TePi0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been going to Austin City Dental for over 6 years. Dr. Cook and his team are incredible, the practice is spotless, All the staff members are unbelievably kind and welcoming. I drive over an hour to get dental work done at this practice, it’s that good.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cybele Diamandopoulos","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLMls3Xnz4kx9pxUIDwDjsVzqgPE5waKsUywS9DneA0daoORw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr Cook is fantastic. A highly skilled practitioner who cares about you as an individual and focuses on giving you the most appropriate, cutting-edge care for what you need without pushing anything that you don’t. His staff is organized, attentive and always  makes you feel seen and cared for. I highly highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Curtis Osterloh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWWjDqBL_zKAscfB24Mo_Wl7768OYGwK2LyQDbAGVqW3YpdJWQHYQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Cook and his staff were very pleasant and professional, and I’m very much appreciated visiting their office.  They were able to confirm I received some bad advice from another dentist office and I immediately switched to Dr. Cook.\n\nI need to update my review to A++.  I recently visited (2/17/26) Dr. Cook’s office to have some bonding on my front tooth replaced.  It was a full hour in the chair.  The good Doc delivered a totally amazing replacement.  I am stunned how good it looks.  Prefect on all fronts.  And he was very particular on the work and extremely detailed.  He wanted perfection and delivered.  Bed side manner was perfect; he checked in with on occasion but focused on my tooth.  Professional still exists! His staff was great as well.  I have found a new Dentist - maybe the best one yet!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Teresa Cue","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJZ0EAWNZUW3hJAAYqdXyO9AUYapEG1gWBH4eOgrEEbgZNc2g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Super competent and professional doctor and staff. My crown was perfectly matched in color and in bite comfort. I’m getting a bridge where there will be 3 crowns so will update then. I will say that the employees seem happy and calm. I think that’s a great reflection of the management.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chase Evans","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKWBnrMowUCH6VHNoSzLe9DMzYV9HKms9LSehOcKIgtkgquXQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dentists are a dime a dozen, but a dentist of Dr. Cook’s caliber is few and far between — he and his team are truly among the best in the city. From the moment you walk in, the professionalism and warmth of his staff stand out. His attention to detail, skill, and genuine care — even during follow-ups — make all the difference. My wife and I feel incredibly fortunate to be under his care and couldn’t recommend this practice more highly.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"William Mohondro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIlymG6CxbNPDKdbgA8ZT7EbKR3C-ZxhwtjDqlizo63blUnHA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It is always a pleasure seeing the professionals at Austin Dental, smiling receptions with recognition upon entry, easy relaxing dental cleaning by Martina and always great seeing and hearing from any of the Doctors.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
