sional, reliable, and genuinely care about your long-term dental health. I had a sudden dental emergency at night and I called there after hours number and they answered me right away. I got to go first thing when they open in the morning and Nicole was absolutely amazing. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nels Arntson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVbx5jwYgYnxELYtaZaDBsbXjKhn_xIwGnr163Z4Dy73DtIZ9Cu9Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Easy to recommend Lifetime Smiles for anyone with dental or cosmetic needs.   Appointments easy to get and texting about details or changes is convenient. Office staff and team all friendly -- easy to talk with about the plan or any questions.  All seem invested in a good experience for patients    Dr. Arzegar is knowledgeable and sincere, listens and explains well.  Our family is glad to have found them.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Christine Oglesby","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL0otS4eCO05Ln-Gw67cGF9cdr0NWHUtHwzFjSTzUwiFUwGfg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been coming to Lifetime Smiles for about 12 years now. Dr. A is wonderful. He is very thorough, explains things carefully, and truly cares about his patients’ health and wellbeing. I always feel very safe and taken care of here. Colleen is so sweet, welcoming, and accommodating. Nicole is a fantastic hygienist, super smart, and I love talking with her. Highly recommended this team.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1whrWQlD8XT4n5LqXNoK725vw42TjXEpFll7OKQY73ynmOzdRZJQlFD1BrO0FaecpQ_joXtwqe8JaezBa7CzrFfvAX2Scdyy-6g5iP3QFUT3Fnw4asXaeDGZGDmfxh4P_liiyZa9Zn1zTp=k-no"],"When":"2025-12-12"},{"Name":"Laura G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJMc4Z6RNwwFsYyNX3yrQsB0gLna6Bn04laG2CyZb9A6cTs_MZY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I cannot recommend Dr. Arzegar and his amazing team enough. From the office team to the hygienists - it’s a team full of amazing humans.\n\nI have had significant anxiety about the dentist and hated going to the dentist for decades. I’ve now been going to Dr. Arzegar for maybe ~10 years and despite now living nearly an hour away from the office, I still make the drive 5+ times per year just to keep him as my dentist.\n\nI recently had an oral appliance made. Dr. Arzegar had noticed I grind my teeth more than normal. Rather than just keep giving me new mouth guards, he recommended I do a sleep study. I had fatigue for decades that no one would listen to because I was a young person of normal weight. Turns out I had sleep apnea. My dental appliance has now shown me a level of rest and recovery I didn’t know even existed. Truly life changing.\n\nThat’s just one example of how Dr. Arzegar goes above and beyond.\n\nHe also did my porcelain veneers, which I get complemented on constantly for their natural yet polished look.\n\nHe also invests in the tools needed to make robust and informed diagnoses.\n\nI never write reviews, but hope this inspires someone to go see Dr. Arzegar and his lovely team.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brooke Harbers","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWw879aFO2LE45jkAfPdsaEJaGC3CIhJivB82hmacbAbmi0y5OB=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"From the moment I walked in I was impressed. Dr A truly took the time to explain everything to me in a way that was easy to understand and incredibly thorough. He noticed things that no one had ever pointed out to me before. The level of detail and care that went into my appointment was amazing. I genuinely felt cared for as a patient.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jon Pilgrim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX-slY-vaU9CPOkWz51BmzbAdz49WL5xbUL2xdcpa5HgGV527yy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a particularly talented and patient dentist. I had to drive back from a Houston trip last week to make an appointment on time and was quite irritable, impatient and just not really ready for the bridge + 2 crowns I was getting done. The Dr and his excellent assistant were patient with me despite all of that. Really a talented dental office (all employees).","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Robert Fletcher","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWFhfIkV52cR647qgO5UWfDEF1hUdr0tj-t8XbAv4Bdk0dL9Bz0WA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been in to lifetime smiles twice now. It started due to a toothache but I quickly found out I had a severe tooth infection. They responded quickly, and my problem was resolved within 72 hours. Their staff is extreme melt friendly and non judgmental, and I would really recommend them to anyone looking for a fresh start and a good experience","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Danine Lareau","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ58nxQnf91Duef3S5W_ajZdOZGS4Octd40xJ9kPrQN6ISL1Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They are wonderful! I highly recommend lifetime smiles. I came in for a broken tooth and it ended up being an almost 2 month process to fix my mouth. They were so helpful and present every step of the way - calling to check on me and offering free cleanings and checkups. I highly recommend these folks. I HATE going to the dentist… And they made this experience very comfortable and pleasant. Thank you guys!!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
