yo muy sastifechos de la Atención y servicio. 🙏","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Esteban Rodriguez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIOeWecafexg2UbHvVGksW8uB7nobZZzUn1xqV47Ll-vSaPMg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Peters is an exceptionally astute as well as a genuinely caring dentist.  She has very impressive credentials and what I consider to be just the right amount of experience.  She has completely restored my trust in the dental profession -relieving me of much stress and anxiety after some less than pleasant experiences elsewhere.  Teresa, my hygienist, was personable, attentive, intelligent, and thorough -carefully noting all of my concerns so that Dr. Peters could address each one.  The front desk staff were professional and courteous as well.  I consider myself to be very lucky to have landed with her practice.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brittany Jinnette","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJvl2J2QqzXLTDp9keYpSUsu_wzSSi7991ELhjNw7_5-hdUiw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Finding a good dentist is so much harder than it should be. Northland Dental was recommended to me by my previous dentist in Seattle and I’m so grateful. Even after moving almost an hour north of Austin, I still make the drive to this office and refuse to switch. The dentists here take their time to explain recommendations and make sure you understand what’s going on, do excellent work, provide helpful tips, and even gave me advice on taking care of my babies teeth and when to find a pediatric dentist. And their hygienists are so friendly and knowledgeable.  100/10 recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ben Schuman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL8JA-kdfatAz2-1yCL74jYVGaTxHbxls3OLyNmfTtLoumUGA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Peters and the Northland staff get an A+. She ended up going with a lower cost treatment than what was originally diagnosed after beginning my treatment which I really appreciate. I could also tell that she took the time to do everything right versus rushing. Overall great experience with my three visits here so far.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"kristen raven","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWc-stwASe9Yk1P5Dj_jcvYmdDoRFVExYnj4tNIKL_EZNrQ8KeL=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I will be recommending Northland dental studio to everyone I know. I was impressed by the friendly and professional front desk  staff, the incredibly knowledgeable and kind dental hygienist, and my new favorite dentist, Dr. Peters. Everyone was efficient and very thorough. I’ve always thought of going to the dentist as a chore and this was actually really enjoyable. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"RL Rhyne","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLJAMRnMoemkmmIl2arnF8FqhEVXApFSavDd4ZOEp8_XoCaRg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This was my initial visit. Martha was great at the front desk. Teresa, the hygienist, was very skillfull and efficient with a bubbly personality. She also had a very light hand with her intruments. Dr. Tibbitts was extremely personable and was punctual with her exam and thorough  with her explanation. The facility and equipment were up to date and very clean. I will definitely be returning in the future.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kayla Williams-Dinardo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbRiD301HFKqIzHDJhkhzLQWhpXc6WorDYj1BBmkIahdCY7mi2=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been a patient of Dr. Mary Kate Peters for two years, and she has never once disappointed me. She is incredibly detail-oriented, truly a perfectionist, and it shows in every part of her work. My smile looks fantastic, and I’m so grateful for her skill and expertise. I have so much respect for her as a dentist. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tali