entistry","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Gender-neutral restroom","enabled":true},{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"crowd","name":"Crowd","options":[{"name":"LGBTQ+ friendly","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Deb Wilson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXeobip-9IjYgaKp1uoU2pCG1PUjm2WgjiAEJat7394gSQXA1xd=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a dental emergency but no dentist in Austin. I feel extremely fortunate to have found South Austin Dental Associates.  Everyone in the practice was kind, welcoming, helpful and good at their jobs.  The office staff worked me in quickly, and then helped with my insurance.  Dental Asst. Heather got me set up and then Dr. Elhosary not only put me at ease while discussing my choices, but then very skillfully handled my situation. I felt very well taken care of both physically and emotionally.  I am happy to now have them as \"my\" dentist's office and recommend them without reservation.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Eric U","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVr0hpOsBLKCIfTxm1Y7gzSPNtn2skeT5Avuj_yp4KsXxuTN29X6w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I can't say enough good things about South Austin Dental. Before finding them, I had visited half a dozen dentists, and none came close to the level of care, professionalism, and genuine compassion I’ve experienced here. My teeth were worn down to nubs, and I was extremely embarrassed about my smile. From the moment I walked in, I knew I was finally in the right place.\n\nDr. Evan Matthysse, Amy, Roger, and the entire team are absolutely incredible. They treat you like a person, not just a patient. You can tell they truly care about what they do and the people they help. I’m currently wearing temporary arches, and even those are amazing—they’ve already made such a difference in my confidence and appearance.\n\nThe quality of work, attention to detail, and kindness I’ve received have all been exceptional. I’m so grateful to have found this team and highly recommend them to anyone who’s looking for top-notch dental care from people who truly care.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1eXjUycaYmHNNt-8QXJ0JH2SlCUs7ByZMPXqsMTwhfpQLtuB_PmugrWKaXLzXI8egKwVxp7epcDPa92ZCr7LY3nEzFsD98gIxHOtFMk0xLvrHl-p4EnpWj8Ntp8X6GG2Cy3YmHuOiEHtw6=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1h_ZrviobzBVxloFWoXFfDdHtcp8ACo_KrhGIrHDszPV5MScEZXfKzWKKEzGHg8RdBpdPmb0YLPyJ4v8E2ERgZePW7iqUlIxRxvXsicFXQKT0YginWLmgq2jhhaydtmpVz_muv9auhiKOw=k-no"],"When":"2025-7-5"},{"Name":"J K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWR98OvgmBba2RjiivqwvaTp2R4tIAYT47Sk61PRL1LMekdPAWO=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I came here because I was having issues with my teeth from recent dental work done. I refuse to continue with current dentist and needed help.\n\nMy initial experience with the front desk was great when making my first appointment. She was personable and empathetic. I was able to get in for a consult quickly.\n\nI consulted with the dentist and he asked if I would like an antibiotic called in and I said yes. The tech took my pharmacy information.\n\nIt was a few days later when I had not heard from the pharmacy for pick up that I decided to call to find out what happened. Turns out, it was not called in.\n\nI came here for help and I’ve been through enough with dentists. I’m thankful I was shown right away that this will not be the dentist I am going to for help.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Norma Archibald","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJxfAhFzCpn5TDhd0onRvNNQHRhSmpycNj64n-_IiFU6Wq6uA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had my first visit today, after my dentist of 37 years retired. I tried two other dentists before finding South Austin Dental Associates. I was impressed with the friendly environment, and the professional staff, who took care of my every need-answered questions, addressed comfort levels (I'm a nervous patient) and had affordable options for necessary dental work. I felt clear about what work was needed and why, and and what to prioritize. My dental hygienist Kaylie was so friendly and gentle, and put me at ease right away, and Dr. Vogelsong was great at explaining everything, and built my confidence in his skill and understanding.Stephanie was amazing and kind in helping me understand the dental plan options and scheduling.  I'm very relieved to find a place that is a good fit for my personal needs, and a place that is up on the latest in technological tools and procedures.If you need a dentist with an impressive dentistry team, look no further, this is it.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Steffan Ihegboro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJtEpxrwaVvZT8t35scx55YOuy0O8EIfbtQ7s3i8QpZ_ll29kg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a great experience at South Austin Dental! My cleaning was thorough and very educational. Dr. Elhosary walked me through my Invisalign plan with clear expectations and timelines. The entire staff is super friendly, efficient, and they made everything easy from check-in to follow-up. This has easily been the best and highest quality dental experience I’ve ever had!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Joel Godfrey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX5HrVRkeYO6zYJtyly5rm0h8wpJZoaMR61ROGDrtvlcB5JP-I=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"South Austin Dental Associates was professional, pleasant and very friendly! They are very knowledgeable in what I was experiencing and put together a well structured plan to get me the treatment I need. Their facility is clean and the staff is very helpful in assisting me with all of my needs. I’ve been to many other dentist before and have never received the kind of treatment I did here. I highly recommend their services for anyone looking for a great dentist office with a great experience!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mike Demerath","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXE5rviR3FkRG8HeCFEp5gRNJIPk0aBos5Y1c4Iuu7UMTydrhSTLA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very efficient and great service. The hygienist was very friendly and professional during my cleaning. Also gave great advice to help my at-home care. The office also gives ample reminders so that you don't forget your appointment. I would highly recommend this practice.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Janie Contreras","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXyLsW4q6BuUjsO9JE42aq4VCsFPUO7Iq_qWu1G-CjdULwr3UiDOg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"From the checkin with the receptionist to the hygienist to checkout the whole staff was very friendly. Susan took her time to explain today's process. The doctor was very informative and gave me hope to regaining my confidence.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
