,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"110936584178440778793","name":"little house dentistry (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110936584178440778793"},"complete_address":{"borough":"South Lamar","street":"2205 S Lamar Blvd","city":"Austin","postal_code":"78704","state":"Texas","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Gayla Harris","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVkmlce5ix_Lr0mU-d4T0RiOdnnp6qm1liEJ_RypZFuKij96Lk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love going in to Little House Dentistry. The friendly welcome is beyond compare and there’s always a ripple of laughter floating through the hallways and in the office.  The level of care is equally phenomenal:  thorough explanations, delicate handling of one’s delicate tissues, polite and respectful interactions and all in service to super healthy teeth and gums. I look forward to seeing my dentist!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gibrán Lule-Hurtado","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXC2prc9ohqe2S-43z5jFaNZLVYeznFBwTXV9pJypn-WpRGW9KmHw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've had top-notch attentive care by dentists abroad but hadn't found a similar experience or a dentist I love in this country -- until now! From the moment I phoned and first visited Little House, the entire team made me feel welcome and cared for. Maddie and Sonya at the front desk were super personable and quick to resolve my scheduling and insurance limitations; they are patient, knowledgeable, and genuinely kind, which made getting established at a new practice so simple and painless.\n\nAli (the only hygienist I will willingly see now) provided exemplary care with a very personal touch. I appreciated him taking time to explain everything I was unsure about and sharing options and honest recommendations. Kim and Dr. Pham are highly skilled, attentive, quick yet thorough, and clearly dedicated to providing the best possible care.\n\nIt’s rare to find a dental office where everyone, from the administrative team to the clinical staff, works so seamlessly together and truly cares about their patients’ comfort and experience. Little House Dentistry is a gem in Austin — I’m so grateful to have found them and can't recommend them highly enough. ^__^","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Richard Davis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWFbB4-EGXO0lecPfVBZugJl42Xui6fTn2UcPsd58OU5tLw2TXxFQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I simply cannot recommend Little House Dentistry loud enough.\n\nFrom the moment I arrived, the practice was charming and inviting—it's literally a cozy little house. The abundance of plants and unique decor immediately signals that this is a place dedicated to care, not just dentistry. As someone who usually feels nervous at the dentist, I immediately felt at ease and part of the family.\n\nThe staff is truly top-notch. Dr. Pham was kind, bubbly, and incredibly thorough, making the entire experience a breeze. Their hygienist, Ali was also clearly experienced, not to mention exceptionally gentle and took the time to check in, ensuring both my comfort and full understanding of my oral health along the way.\n\nUnlike practices where I feel rushed in and out, Little House made it clear that my health and comfort are their top priority. The difference is night and day.\n\nI just can't believe it took me this long to make the switch!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Suzanne Harrison","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocINIo8uX6TcvUMxivBzW7vwe8srzGCT1hNOzQA0VfeJzVJY-g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love the hygienist, whose name escapes me. He does an excellent job scraping my teeth and is very funny. Good to laugh when at the dentist. Dr. Fam was thorough and took pictures of areas in my mouth that will need care in the future. I have been going to Little House Dentistry for a number of years and always felt comfortable.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jimmy Stanley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKJxj7t4v8w_a3B27wd7mvTcxQ3Cyikdu93IcVHHl2DWDShjw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hong Van was professional and thorough in every way. She did a great job in attending to my teeth. She made me feel comfortable in the chair.  I certainly want to choose her again.  Jimmy Stanley","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Julia Aneighbor","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ29QpWEpEZUdefha1ag70UEHCj-w0P_MJg0Ha1-IasS0dEGA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As a dentalphobe, I have had nothing but positive experiences over my last several years at Yellow House Dentistry. Great care with a soul. ❤️","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Silke Morin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWf8t3XBZFMQJkifFf9GDH0rY4dyz9ToTL_4HO1NzKJlN2FVFZ4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have always had extremely positive experiences at Little House Dentistry - from routine cleanings to dental emergencies. Dr. Nothern and her staff are top notch!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"April Solloway","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK_o2VaAyOEvLRLtYC1ew7Wlkigkd-pfezxK9PueMZX9FvWKA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It took me a minute to find a dentist in Austin that I liked and trusted and I think the 3rd (4th?) time is the charm. From my initial call to the ladies at the front desk, to Ali, the hygienist, and ending w Dr. Pham...I can not complain.  Not only can I not complain, I believe I have found MY dentist and will happily refer ALL my friends and family their way.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
