’t try to up-sale me procedures that I didn’t need. I definitely found my new dentist..","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jamie LaRue","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX5cQk4I-gTEJBc6rs5MwvOipCyGLyAhHhoz8wrNmcH3WilpmVYkQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been searching for a new dentist since my long-time dentist stopped taking my insurance. I've been through 3 different new dentists and have not been entirely satisfied with any of them-- one was too far away, one tried to talk me into a bunch of unnecessary procedures, and one had newbie staff that didn't seem to know what they were doing.  Feeling desperate, I went to Moontower Dental because it got great reviews and took my insurance. I think I have finally found my dentist! The staff were personable and efficient, the dentist was competent and honest, and the environment was comfortable and very Austin-y. The great music and decor also help!   Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cinnabelle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUJNm36gaLAU2YhXhWaAruXssZcL3AeqSRVmmGW-B0AFB-4G0I=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been terrified of dentists since I was a teen and had my first painful encounter with a dentist.  As a result I would neglected my dental health until it becomes an emergency.  Then I found Dr. Gillett and his staff at Moontower.\n\nDr. Gillett one of the most compassionate and caring people I have ever met but he is also one of a handful of dentist I trust.  His gentle manner extends to the rest of his practice as his entire staff is gentle and kind.  I am grateful.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kevin Orput","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKRCvXTm0Ut53EVD6TONRvw-8WVNP3gYrPDwQRgz0UYBemFSqk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am terrified of dental work and, for that reason, have avoided anything dental related for years. After a few very painful experiences, I just couldn’t bring myself to go in. I was referred to Dr Gillett / Moontower and finally made an appointment, expecting to pay the price for years of neglect. I was so incredibly pleasantly surprised with the experience. The team was amazing, I was in and out, no cavities, for the record… it was really incredible and I definitely recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ingrid Jone","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXXZSxN0h84TPyeiq6k6vyQk1EMvKFonvzYPCDNzeEOuE1EKRmD=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great dentist if you're scared of going! The entire staff makes you feel so comfortable and safe, and my visits are always super quick while also getting all my questions answered. Definitely would recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aly Comstock","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVeh-n0geA0aI3Ysv3eE_Dm-_8CCgVQz05S2K0KaxLy7yGshY0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I like that it’s a local small hometown dentist and not corporate. I would recommend this place as I felt the opinions of the dentist were accurate. He doesn’t upsell . I’ll let you know how my filling experience goes. The cleaning was very fast but not the most comfortable one I’ve had but it was definitely quick which is a plus . Love the receptionist too such a vibe!\n\nUpdate:\nHad a lose filing so he replaced it . Quick and virtually painless . Would recommend this place 10/10","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chelsea White","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUgCrXVA0BkiPNePuEGCGIVRN7wcYpbLf6sriT2WWdLqdTdu73GlA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The Moontower Dental team is amazing! While going to the dentist is no one's favorite thing to do, Lance and his team make it enjoyable and quick. The office is fun and beautiful with gorgeous plants, a mortal combat console, and cool art throughout. The team then quickly takes care of your teeth, addresses any issues, and treats you with care and compassion. I would recommend Moontower to anyone and everyone!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Andrew “yongi” Trent","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVzs8IkVd2ngZplst_Ix71-5utyW9O4yyfbEE4CZwqjRoWeAxia=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fantastic folks from the front desk to the guy sticking his hands in your mouth. An easy-access location, no hassle upfront clarity on costs (if there are any, depending of course on your insurance), and a cool vibe to boot. What's not to love about this independent dental office? Highly recommended if you're sick of the conglomerate practices that seem to exist mostly to sell veneers and such.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
