tile.gps\u0026w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=39.859127\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"111381630337351369406","name":"Austin Dental Specialty Group (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111381630337351369406"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Brodie Lane","street":"5000 Davis Ln #101","city":"Austin","postal_code":"78749","state":"Texas","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Cosmetic dentistry","enabled":true},{"name":"Emergency services","enabled":true},{"name":"Pediatric care","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"crowd","name":"Crowd","options":[{"name":"LGBTQ+ friendly","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Gregory Diseker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVMYVxbRgmKndtPtLjRoIamRtV1Ch3HsliIJxYd32lw9JoOJH4c=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve spent over 20 hours in the dental chair these past several months, and every single minute was worth it because of Dr. Brossart. She is hands-down one of the best dentists I’ve ever been seen by. Not only is she incredibly skilled, but she’s also one of the kindest and friendliest people you’ll ever meet.\n\nHer work gave me a brand-new smile, and I genuinely can’t thank her enough for the confidence and happiness it’s brought me. She’s a millennial with many, many years ahead of her to keep making people in Austin smile — literally. Anyone who gets the chance to be her patient is lucky.\n\nIf you’re looking for a dentist who does exceptional work and treats you like a real human being, go see Dr. Brossart. She’s awesome.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"roxana khoroushi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVBjEOlQYmQKj8E9ltytBOVsNQjOPtKIbFqFVBmmY7XkTs5-xU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I first heard about Dr. Brossart’s office through a friend, and it turned out to be one of the best decisions I’ve made. From my very first visit, I knew I could trust this office, caring, knowledgeable, and truly invested in their patients’ well being. I’ve seen both Dr. Brossart and Dr. Behmanesh, and they are both amazing! Each of them takes the time to listen, explain, and make you feel comfortable and cared for. The entire team is professional, kind, and welcoming. I couldn’t be happier to be a patient here and highly recommend this office to anyone looking for exceptional care!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Syree Cc","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUE91sGUb-JIjiSuzhjwiPyqAcyRq2sMr4AvObO-wI1DEE934k=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ 10/10\nAbsolutely the best dental experience I’ve ever had! Especially after 20+years of navy dental work.\nDr. Brossart was amazing from start to finish. She has such a warm and friendly demeanor that instantly puts you at ease. The atmosphere in her office was calm and welcoming, and her team made me feel genuinely cared for.\nShe took her time during my filling, explaining each step and making sure I was completely comfortable. I didn’t feel a thing the entire session, which is saying a lot for someone who usually dreads dental work!\nI left not only pain-free but actually smiling. 😊\nHands down, the best dentist I’ve been to thus far, and I’d totally recommend Dr. Brossart to anyone looking for exceptional care with a personal touch.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Roxanne Duvall","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWuMCG8CmkV2AyW-K9IfWHRRGoWz6r9RAuZoIExYyZdW3XEpWogIw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"When my temporary crown made by another provider fell off just a few hours, I contacted Austin Dental Specialty Group and they got me in the next day.\n\nAlejandra, the assistant who created my new temp, was top notch. She is experienced, highly skilled, and has an absolutely lovely demeanor.\n\nShe worked well with Dr Brossart who came off as kind, efficient, genuine, and down to earth.  Thank you Ladies for expediency and care. Much appreciated. -Roxy","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nathan Churchill","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVxYWeN9RH2Z8wUBQY8Gh-QMOylg44ECv8W3rGQa1DYzLS-CVEvRg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Brossart was awesome about helping me with anxiety I get at the dentist. She was patient with me and worked through my uneasiness very calmly. It was one of the better experiences I've had getting a filling. The steps they take to alleviate pain and anxiety are incredibly helpful and it makes for a much better experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Annie Santiago","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKqrv19hzj8cjuQD2wBKkD5y05gcfjSWb23in1MhmsJt2YhHA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I heard about Dr. Brossart’s office through a friend, and it was truly the best decision I’ve made. I’ve been a long-time patient now, and I couldn’t be happier with the care I receive. Dr. Brossart is kind, professional, and very conservative with her treatments—she never recommends anything unnecessary and always takes the time to explain every detail. The entire team is friendly, welcoming, and makes every visit comfortable. I completely trust Dr. Brossart and highly recommend her to anyone looking for an amazing dentist!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Samantha Alvarado","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIO5eelIEZaUdmAbVzZZ5iq4omdQZLmmgD6JuWAeJWAQZbsTg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been a long-term patient of Dr. Brossart, and I can’t recommend her enough! She’s an amazing dentist. Very knowledgeable, gentle, and most importantly, conservative in her approach. She never pushes unnecessary treatments and always takes the time to explain everything clearly. The entire team is warm, professional, and makes every visit comfortable. I truly trust Dr. Brossart with my dental care and wouldn’t go anywhere else!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"jl welsh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK_S-L01_Y27A1Oi46b3YBruRIkxyVqPXVEThXTpGCi-N2gAA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This appointment was an outsource from the VA. At check in i was pleasantly greeted and signed in. The dentist and her entire staff were wonderful people, and caring. I would highly recommend this office to anyone needing dental care, they are very good.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
