tle":"Videos","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAECo3V1ZGxxulEkw2CAJ1hEWYZI89O2nGKgz5Ja4iMkOvtEE6o2En4dVe3eB7FwsAUQIMr32337Fqq8GJh1x6hG2ih9NDfCegXe-qIDErDf9DfEVJgRHJtdqTSW0GvBt770GCI=w529-h298-k-no"},{"title":"Street View \u0026 360°","image":"https://streetviewpixels-pa.googleapis.com/v1/thumbnail?panoid=Zkfoc8G6tNBToq8f4SKmnQ\u0026cb_client=maps_sv.tactile.gps\u0026w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=125.25149\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"101527363805090571618","name":"Perspective Dental: Ashley Smitherman, DDS (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101527363805090571618"},"complete_address":{"borough":"North Loop","street":"4631 Airport Blvd Suite 120A","city":"Austin","postal_code":"78751","state":"Texas","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"from_the_business","name":"From the business","options":[{"name":"Identifies as women-owned","enabled":true}]},{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Onsite services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Cosmetic dentistry","enabled":true},{"name":"Emergency services","enabled":true},{"name":"Pediatric care","enabled":true},{"name":"Sedation dentistry","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"crowd","name":"Crowd","options":[{"name":"LGBTQ+ friendly","enabled":true},{"name":"Transgender safespace","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Jade Perkins","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXU0HZv7PmkR9NKjuDydI64lRJBpOT6aRR8b_4eRgTlAjTPxmO4JA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had an amazingggg dental assistant, Juliet! Was so welcoming and ven thhough she knew i worked in dentistry she stayed so informational and professional! She really set the tone for a great appointment. Hygienist was amazing tooo very kind and great cleaning !! I think Elena. Doc was great too! Kind, thourough and conservative approach. Front Office ladies were great too! Thanks yall","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Karina Garza","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX4CV4LNqYlT9fhy1UiKPmFtqrfXRDkYA0MHICsKz-CuIxinjdy=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Been a patient for around three years or so, originally found them on an r/Austin thread asking about recommendations for places that are very sensitive and patient, especially about sensory issues. Every single person is so lovely and kind, I always feel welcome. The reminder texts are so, so helpful for someone like me. I’ve gotten cleanings, X-rays, and even two wisdom teeth extracted in office. All ez-pz. Dr. Smitherman is kind, efficient, and straight forward. I always know what’s going on. Super responsive via call and text. The sunglasses and headphones during appointments is a game changer. Never felt more taken care of. Hope my work doesn’t ever change insurance, as I’m covered here and feel so pampered!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bonnie Olden","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKG9fC8f4yLOs0_f7A7swYSgv25GlgNea8Np3kFd4zdgH7R7w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"From the front admin ladies to the dental hygienist assistants in the back and Dr. Smitherman herself, the whole experience is amazing! I enjoy coming here and have referred others like my husband and child to come here. Even when I need fillings and to talk about what is going on with my teeth, this thorough team makes me feel comfortable to ask all the questions and gain confidence I am making good decisions about my teeth. The flexible staff makes it easy to get appointments, even when booked. They talk to me about my teeth needs and preferences when scheduling my next appointment b/c not everything in life maked that a convenient choice. They may not be equipped to do all things dental like root canals, but they have referred me to excellent surgical dentist who are just as amazing. They also have a wonderful price cut program if you are self pay. They try to think of everything to make dental life better.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Samantha Tran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUa1apyvcxqkbpSmSVvescOmkbw3nIZlEqQCZgLpFkNDdX61-MmuQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My husband and I have been going to Perspective Dental for 5 years and love it!\n\nDr. Smitherman has helped me pinpoint some sensitivity on my teeth and fix it with a new brushing technique.\n\nElena H. has been my dental hygienist all 5 years and not only do my teeth feel so clean afterwards, but I also get to catch up with her.\n\nLove Perspective Dental, I have recommended them to many friends and family.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ashley Manter","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW7Niq3DWaTpU_AkYhf3iMArYy-ADnvlQ8_sM9n5x0jyGAlTLZJ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been coming to this practice for many years, and now my entire immediate family goes here as well. The team is consistently kind and welcoming from the moment you walk in. They always take the time to explain everything thoroughly and ensure we are comfortable. Highly recommend for anyone looking for a dentist who truly cares!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jaclyn N. Sepp","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX2qdH9W9Vjzb7BSxCr9nvvacCHU4c3l9dI1OYOjwHM4drWRv3kYw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is hands-down the best dental office I’ve ever been to. From the moment you walk in, you’re greeted with warmth and kindness, and the whole team makes you feel like family. They’re incredibly accommodating, patient, and thoughtful, and you can tell they truly care about their patients and the quality of their work. I always leave feeling taken care of — highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"amber weems","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJTlIP9mnYA_jjpfvKEl5d8_Qi3MBgafWODc4ZzQlRDh7uwKg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After years of dental problems, multiple dentists, and several failed outcomes, I finally reached out to the team at Perspective Dental. They got me in quickly for an exam and helped me develop a reasonable and affordable treatment plan. The staff were extremely friendly and welcoming, and always just a phone call away to answer my many questions.\n\nAfter my exam with Dr. Smitherman, we created a plan to restore my smile and address the years of dental issues I had. My treatment required multiple visits and a lot of time for both myself and the staff — but it was absolutely worth it!\n\nDr. Smitherman, Melissa, Juliet, and Jasmine (just to name a few of the incredible team members) took care of me like family. They were just as invested in my progress as I was, cheering me on every step of the way.\n\nMy dental work is now complete, and I’m thrilled to say I have no more dental pain, a smile I’m proud to show in family pictures, and an overall boost in self-confidence. I’ll continue to see them for regular care and will also be transitioning other family members to their practice.\n\nIf you have any dental concerns, I highly recommend Dr. Smitherman and her team — you won’t be disappointed!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aenne","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVbMPsMp4XyyLzFdh4rpzlxhjb4jMQ9GX4hXAA1CWzLp4d4y-s=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My insurance changed in the new year and I was really anxious about going to a new practice in the middle of some dental issues. I cannot say more positive things about my experience with Nikki, my dental hygienist. She was incredibly empathetic and made sure all my concerns were heard. She helped me understand what care I needed, and was a great conversationalist during my cleaning. She's a gem!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
