"Pediatric care","enabled":true},{"name":"Sedation dentistry","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Gender-neutral restroom","enabled":true},{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"crowd","name":"Crowd","options":[{"name":"LGBTQ+ friendly","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Tracy Bowie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUWEDyTDLWNHWwqkZ9CsMff8F36n7k2t1XN15RVuXHefWTs9Zuy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The dental work is great here and the dentists themselves are kind and compassionate BUT they run very shady billing processes. I was not communicated with in any way that insurance didnt cover part of my procedure and now months later getting a call from collections saying I owe money. Complete bullshit and I would have been able to take a care of it from the begining with one simple call from their office. I will never use any swish dental office or dentist again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michele McDermott","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI7WRwBY5PZceAea5D-zRq0w8SuZwRqYuGVo9fLYqOeKIg5VBE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My experience has been fantastic from my first contact with the office to schedule a new patient appointment through the consultation and treatment plan provided by Dr. Suzie Palacios. All of the staff are professional and help make the experience positive and welcoming. If you are looking for a new dental practice with state of the art care and a caring team, I recommend Swish Dental at Bull Creek.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Pags","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYyQ19x_bxJI2S1i4VFEMyRtkw1MhfWE1mX0moAxU3czttFSJ7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was very impressed with how smooth the team had handled a cavity. I had my concerns, of course, who doesn’t? The doctor and team were very thorough in explaining everything to me and was maybe a 20 minute process to fill the cavity. Best part, didn’t feel a thing!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alyssa Ruiz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIdPMxF0ycoDLapIdZNu7h-nBpclThUgPXqpzcPvyRvfT60yQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This place is dodgy. They told me I couldn’t choose a regular cleaning covered by my insurance and had to do a deep cleaning instead. At my first appointment, the hygienist started taking scans I’d already done, then said she didn’t even have time for my cleaning, so I rescheduled.\nAt the second appointment, they made me pay upfront, started 10 minutes late, and the ‘deep cleaning’ lasted only barely 15 minutes without even touching my gums. When I called to ask why it was so quick, they said it varies and I ‘didn’t have much buildup,’ despite insisting I needed a deep cleaning at an extra cost. They even offered to redo it because of how short it was. I’m now disputing the charge through my HSA","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"air vista","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKW5GIJCN-yI-FZrhufqhGU9jXAYURIjIeohLOIel8XrfUfaQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"They misuse your insurance and leave you with bills that should not be. I would not recommend it trust them. They have billed both my husband's and my insurance without consent claiming service charges on both and in the end the service I was covered for I was sent a bill for nearly $500. The service is not great either. Will not go again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jordan Worm","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXoAvmQldBhDRz5OoWEmYt3YzTCEhMELh-0XTGxxYyJBJu3CTdE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Pros: Very nice staff, Dr. is willing to work with you, and decent facility.\n\nCons: They are an Invisalign seller first, and a dentist's office second. Also, be prepared for a second charge of $750, which is \"In your contract,\" to get your retainers after you drop thousands on the treatment. I remember being told the up front cost covered all of the treatment, but those pesky contracts. The whitening experience was not great, and there was a lot of gum exposure to the bleach.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lise Marcantonio","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUVckIs94kJpa0CPcTVyEkGycIvdG1XXS0IdxHFmPhw3OY_Lns=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After an accident in 2001, I have had an incredibly fragile jaw. Anytime I have work done, it is both extraordinarily stressful and painful. I unexpectedly had major work done yesterday. Their staff’s sincere caring and skill was so reassuring, I didn’t stress at all. Work went far more smoothly than I ever imagined it could. I went to the Bull Creek location. Dr Marmurek was amazing! If more stars were an option they would still have all of them!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Megan Colon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVMoTtTe5GstNaXpHUxvSsdn79Qz2fu-l4n05OYkxVUhpX81mLDwQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is the best dentist’s office I have ever been to!! Every staff member is SO kind and the atmosphere when you walk in is so peaceful and inviting. 100 percent recommend 😊","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
