:"Windsor Hills","street":"1015 E Braker Ln #2","city":"Austin","postal_code":"78753","state":"Texas","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Sedation dentistry","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Craig Matlock","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVWzgMS9Vr0v_OVwY2SpS0e_FWa65kAyxr--3K8FUwHhU1WC1E=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I came here for a one off as I chipped my tooth trying to fix a key ring…yes I’m aware that was stupid, but that’s beside the point. I came here for what I deemed an emergency and they got me right the same day. That brief transaction made me a fan of this place and I’ve been a client since then. The whole staff is always a1 and they treat you with so much organic kindness. Just got my braces done today (shoutout to Jennifer and Doc Sheinbein) and I couldn’t be any happier. Y’all got me for life!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Johnny King","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_YX1z352aEAS4VN8ewlGcwvUY9P7x8GUsYYrHD1hEzgBY0kX8Qw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jennifer has an amazing caring approach to her job. Best cleaning I can remember having in decades. Dentist was non nonsense, detailed, and also non invasive. I give 5 stars as I cannot remember the last time I had such a pain free experience. They really care and kept asking how I was doing throughout. You can tell everyone here likes their job and are proficient.\nJennifer is superb for the cleaning ask for her!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Juliana K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUI-lJ9k1h-pCYpSFVZg7xtiCJ3qMuhiznqaLGOlTlxu5V-AHE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They have been my dentist for 12 years. During that time they've only recommended one filling, and the assistant held my hand while they did it. When they weren't accepting my new insurance, they very generously honored it and didn't charge me. They always run on time and have been cleaning my teeth by hand all this time because the cavitron thing made my teeth too sensitive. I can't think of a single complaint I've had with them in all this time.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kristina Reed","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIVY1aM1xATucjwjWdpfMk10YcT7TTKRx92CVSev2LFtwKkDA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wonderful doctor. I trust her ! Im very scared when it comes to work on my teeth, but she will put you at ease.  Also each and everyone of the assistants and ladies at the front are are very very nice and make you feel comfortable !\n\nAgain a hard tooth with a super long root was able to be pulled by my wonderful dentist ! I don’t know how her and her staff make me feel so at ease even with a fear of the dentist . This place is great , they make you feel welcome and want you to make yourself at home. I’ll never go anywhere else. Very professional staff at the front as well as kind and friendly attitudes!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2UzovmLCeMSyrhc_FH9XtKED9VXRJ7BVNphxwqJgenisEeLQS9UcKuQ5t6ARrKVcO72QhaosBtE4hT6I-y_zdjrn3tuPVKe448-Ru8jJWppEeWL2auaCrVmv5D-RjdQ-Ggq8iS=k-no"],"When":"2019-2-22"},{"Name":"Grumpysleeper","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWVTFSdeLJQ0oezaIuE7EddjYOJ4ZL7ZML_AhCkJJtfOcV3rxw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I'm so glad I found this dentist! I went in for a routine cleaning and exam but was nervous to get anything done since I'm 37 weeks pregnant. They made sure not to use anything that was unsafe for me or baby! I felt completely at ease and knew I was in good hands. My teeth feel so clean and I'm glad I went in.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jamie Vasquez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXq_pX5M9m8r_I3GJY1K8DqZqpZGpIORm48G4bv6Wb6bnr2yhWf=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Most amazing and patient DA I have ever had. Nohemi was so sweet and comforting when I told her how nervous and embarrassed I was. The Dr took her time and explained everything to expect and how to plan my procedures. I cried in the chair and they waited and talked me through it. I have never been so comfortable and felt truly listened to at a dental office. This is the only dentist myself, my husband and our Four children will go to. Thank you so much everyone!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"miki","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVjyfOJppc-Xlk5PSNlzmNHfYg0e3-cwv2mIMljBexoWP0okpTZCQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr Zayed is AMAZING. She’s funny, patient, and very thorough. She explained what all my X-rays meant, was gentle in the exam/cleaning, and made me feel safe. The wait time in the office was minimal. The staff were all kind and accommodating. I highly recommend this dentist and office.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gabe Link","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWTUw4bFR9E4oyjDXAlrqDTxVvZiHzT8V-pSYKyVTe5FU2yjo_eVA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We've been coming here before our kids had teeth and they've always been so kind and friendly. Dr. Sheinbein has always so gentle that the kids actually look forward to going to the dentist. All the staff is awesome. Thanks!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2hXCQqCI_1CiDJoSgBEu55WOyhDoeXHCkyv1MdhxbtidwbHuLMvbPHSaoX3niqhE6nS9QUpCUMf1sHQXkWjbC1uTbY3HMlE_OWYgFrHwOa0tCCJupJJaJVYGRfkUJFIm3-_s3ffw=k-no"],"When":"2021-9-8"}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
