bBsaiW-CACEEkEhjA0-0ikFRA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nice and small homey feel. They treat you like family! Everyone is so kind and personable. My kids and I had a great experience! They are always so happy and excited for their appointment and eager to see Dr.Munis, as you can see their expressions in the waiting area :)","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3H7O8B3WhVMh02QWxGfXwgI5IYI8ojK9MpaB_iY0Xat95SkOgmrvbvcOI8KMSa5khsbKXsYrNv-Yat54YVwy0VWwVyR-5RK3Oz1S2Yfms2-fmItpiH2oEsb3bh8ds7QVh9pSHlDn_YSyk=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2ylbiuAy_ipOyAL5kDr5x1az83voKjEP_saaGBBLtTl_Cy81uMW08rY9JJR-3iuka6HvkL1d7qF6BnXjAsMeZP1UKE9deNJzH5gU4u7dD0ORfHVxNpIprgKc4QPF9AEC9GLPae0JI5IdJ6=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-3"},{"Name":"Dheeraj Kumar G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIv6v0KLqBFn9cIjVyXVjXrTyFQcJ49gr1zvfxQWfl1BtOR-A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a wonderful experience with Dr. Munis and her office. She is extremely friendly, honest, and very transparent about treatment options. Dr. Munis took the time to explain the entire procedure in detail and made sure I understood what was happening at every step, which really put me at ease. The staff was welcoming and professional, and the overall environment felt comfortable and well cared for. I truly appreciated the attention and care I received and would highly recommend Dr. Munis to anyone looking for a dentist who is knowledgeable, patient, and genuinely cares about her patients.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Eyosias Samson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL3q2IjZd4xK3y9S2jx8JPDyEZsu1kdAYLk6LOYy0Dv_YKzPw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr Munis, Val, and the staff here at Snow Dental were great! I’ve seen multiple dentists over the years and this was the most thorough and helpful interaction I’ve ever had. They were careful to explain what they were doing and why. They were able to look at my teeth and tell me my dental history without previous info. The location is also super convenient. Super easy to go stop by Central market for some delicious gelato after I feel good about my teeth being cleaned :) I trust their opinion and look forward to continuing to come to Snow with my family.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sana Mohammed","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVAgZA2x5PQTQpq4VFpjWweBU5jjfoG_iPAE8MH7QYjkZYERFlUEg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been to a bunch of different dentists over the years and this one has been the best! Dr. Munis was incredible. It’s the best cleaning I’ve had in yearssss! She did such a good job gettingg my teeth super cleaned and she was very thoughtful and nice given it is uncomfortable to get your teeth cleaned. Her dental assistant Jessica was so kind and wonderful! Very grateful to have found such a great denist in Austin!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tommy Moriarty","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKMsE3O4qfydDjpfUczZDHHTz2_3LSFpQezNPQXpOPjXIRln4YZ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Munis and Jessica did a great job with my cleaning! Dr. Munis took time explaining everything to me and gave me a plan to keep my teeth healthy going forward. The staff at the office were all great as well. I'm very happy I found this dentist and will definitely be back!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"ali kodwavi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLiMSZ9iodVRBrqghWN1zoNfrGPTURSCwNe7iKr3BwzCgyyTQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Munis is hands down the best dentist I’ve ever been to. She’s incredibly kind, patient, and makes sure you feel comfortable every step of the way. I’ve always been a little anxious about dental visits, but she has such a calm and gentle approach that it completely puts you at ease.\n\nShe takes the time to explain what she’s doing and why, which really builds trust and helps you understand your own dental health better!\n\nI’m so grateful to have found Dr. Munis — she genuinely cares about her patients and it shows in everything she does. I wouldn’t go anywhere else. 10/10","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lubaina Najmi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWU2N7B5hhfAJwugv8AVSGpRAX_-M2Tw6jAIupDmn60d3-PZP2G=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been seeing Dr. Munis for my dental care, and I can honestly say it’s been one of the best experiences I’ve had with any healthcare provider. From the moment you walk in, the staff is welcoming and organized, and Dr. Munis takes the time to explain everything clearly before starting any procedure. You can tell she genuinely cares about her patients comfort and long-term dental health.\n\nWhat stands out the most is her attention to detail and how gentle she is during treatments — even procedures I was nervous about turned out to be quick and painless. The office is clean, modern, and runs on time, which I really appreciate!!!\n\nHighly recommend Dr. Munis to anyone looking for a dentist who is professional, compassionate, and truly excellent at what she does!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"rashida ali","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXw1jlIoux-MTb67GywbjBnqAZZYUH4WUZ2WLSbT-M3P8fxBDau=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Munis and staff are amazing here!! I went there for a consultation because my current hygienist could not reschedule me at the time I had to suddenly travel. I asked Snow Dental and gave me an appointment right away which was AMAZING. I loved their service and will highly recommend them. Beautiful office, friendly staff and great service.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
