:[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free street parking","enabled":true},{"name":"Paid parking lot","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Peter Gregg","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUQPB1OwrTbKSV1QJs8-qQFRYZyaHtqgNZ2K8L0YeDT7vpBVo1I0w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cannot say enough about how great this team was.   Had emergency dental need and was able to get in with short notice.  From the front desk to xrays to hygenist - everyone was incredibly kind, thoughtful and caring.  Dr. Dawson was thorough in discussions on options and consistently checking in on my well being.  They know what they are doing, they care and are very thoughtful in their approach.  Very modern office as well.\n\nEnd of the day - they were able to address the acute issue at hand and will be going to them going forward.\n\nHighly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Angie Palacios","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJMgnqzgujGDWwzYsnb2E_3lnAFy9f3QOGQobdEQI02ZdRpTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This was my first visit to Groovy Dental.  I was slightly overdue for a cleaning, so I was a little nervous, but I had a great Check up and cleaning. I had one old, cracked filling which needed replacing. All of my options were thoroughly and thoughtfully explained to me. They were kind enough to accommodate me and take care of it today. Dr. Dawson and all of the staff I encountered were very kind,  professional and knowledgeable. I feel so lucky to have found them. Oh and the office was very beautiful, clean and comfortable!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"patricia sites","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW_TQFwOH5Ht6t3rjXrWkG1QJnldpyhEwDYLV2e4km220lhC91P=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My appointment was amazing. Front desk were kind and courteous, the staff in the back were so wonderful. I was having a spinal migraine and the doctor helped me get through all of my fillings and I go back Monday to finish my teeth cleaning. But over all my experience was the best dental experience I have ever had and will go back to them on a regular basis to get my teeth clean. If you need your teeth cleaned or anything else please call the office. They have a single and family plans if you don’t have dental insurance.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Wesley McGinty","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU594y2SeQFbhkcNan0fwwaKjXWsuYHNIjBWc5fiTtwNDFC43Mn=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My visit with Groovy Dental today left me feeling as if I had just experienced something out of another period in time, real courtesy.\nTheir staff is not only polite to a fault. They were courteous, professionals in every sense of the word. I found them to be knowledgeable, and informative. I would recommend this team to anyone.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sherryl Hauglum","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV_VljDstB_jlOKjsM6Rh-E5kb-ZjazBM0czzuuVW9lUBIFt75obw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A truly professional and beautiful practice with the latest innovative technology available. The staff was exceptionally kind, took the time to explain everything clearly, and made me feel completely at ease throughout the visit. It honestly could not have been a better dental experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kathy Zarate","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKFnOumClddgkaEd7NrjvWTH8TkfKqBIqiNsynPO32cXyKUBg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I switched a couple of years ago from a national chain dental office to Groovy Dental and couldn’t be happier with that decision. My appointments start on time, I get the correct receipts I need for my FSA reimbursement, and the staff is so friendly and welcoming. All of my questions are answered and it’s very easy to schedule my appointments.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Susanne Utterback","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI2urjj7cAhFMx75pKDAZo6BRuZbQu5TUx3iSxXADYYaYuxDA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great dental office, modern,  clean, staff is very efficient. The dentist gives great advise, is not pushy at all. I had a crown done at the office, last year. The dental work was done without any pain, and the procedure did not last forever. The finished crown proved to be a great fit.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nicole Santeliz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJbIHHf82oYFm7rPf86lezp3p_TTh2Gcry3nJ3oEcrk0hOlCow=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an excellent experience here for my dental cleaning. The entire team was friendly and made me feel comfortable right away. The dentist was great, explained everything clearly, and the appointment was quick and efficient. They use modern tools and technology, which really shows in the quality of care. I’ll definitely be coming back!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
