gender safespace","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Checks","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"James Hopper","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKGdnolrWHxUkprdLkztEBEhx_lVf6Hn4xq_PZq7ry3hT4WDg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Somehow, getting three fillings done was an enjoyable experience!?!?  Dr. Shvets came through on his motto of a pain-free experience and I felt no discomfort.  He and his staff were very thorough and were perfectionists with doing a great job.  You could tell that top quality is the priority and I never felt like they were rushing.\nAlso, the staff was extremely friendly, knowledgeable and professional.\nOverall, a much better experience than it was with my previous dentist, I'll be back for sure.\nHighly HIGHLY RECOMMEND!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Donovan Dunn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXhJAwDXF_3egm65X72RejC_WUD5i3ACC7_AnCv9rRomLirMXvK=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I just came here for the first time earlier today and it was a fantastic experience! I haven’t been to the dentist in a while so I was not sure on what to expect, but they are professionals and keep you in good hands! All the staff are super friendly and use the best technology I have ever seen to ensure your teeth are well taken care of! 5/5 stars and I look forward to coming here for all of my dental work!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Maricela Valencia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWdr_9gGbWhSp0fj_q_qhMGNF-TdmrUHp95FW4alrXj3jZYGnY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had my first appointment here at Craft of Dentistry today as a new patient and everything went really well! I was excited to try them out after reading great reviews. I was due for my 6th month cleaning and everything they did was efficient and done with care. Everyone I talked to was welcoming and happy to be there. We talked about possibly whitening my teeth as well as getting my wisdom teeth removed soon which I am confident I will be taken good care of for that. They all have lots of experience and know how to treat patients with respect. Definitely will recommend them to anyone looking for a new dentist office!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brenda Harte","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJZ2-hz7qM65sPQyXf0lUixRkn7OFSRd3YZh1Wca-mru3kRbQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is great!! So friendly from the front of the office to the back. I needed a new dentist as mine, who I loved, retired. I have had many dentists and I’m pretty picky about them and their staff. I was due for dental visit and found these wonderful people online and read the Google reviews. I popped in a few weeks ago to check it out and made the appointment. I had my visit today and this place deserves its 5 star rating. Plus, it’s such an elegant and modern space. I saw Dr. S. (Yaron Shvets) and he is very professional and knowledgeable yet chill. Very kind and considerate and great at explaining. I’m so happy I found Craft of Dentistry!!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3v_ADZfHcEtlE70pj-pdRinkEPdRlBmPbQ-AdBXzu2cZSVR3SM5tmXf3MdobDQwFnn8xouXN_TCf1hhaCGTC-yB38y6c4OM7FJLzGAhnx028zmVWeDDpX2EtHooZCGqsyfpmteanm2hTs=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2XzOjxRYC6EtqPoICBbbqf1HtSqXIEQVQmlWc6W2Dfo4-0hNVY-4ckjDkJX3wjS2jUp9_L3qXsEe6-DF95agXUZU3ENiJw_IG6t