"Had my first appointment at Craft of Dentistry with Dr. Lyon yesterday and I am so happy I found them! Dr. Lyon is a gem and provided me with great information on preventative care. You can tell the whole team cares about excellence—they even went out of their way to compliment the work of my previous dentist, which was such a nice touch. The atmosphere is professional, the staff is lovely, and the care is top-tier. A 5-star experience from start to finish!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mary Avalos","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUIFWo1ZufJnC_2uhJRI-fzVW6LJLvBKhadklPbQTsQ6dv8UshIAA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This was my fisrt time coming to this place and I had a great experience. I haven't been to a dentist in about 3 years so I was a bit nervous. They have a warm welcoming environment when I first walked in. One of the hygienist came and gave me a tour of the place and walked me to my chair. They made me feel very calm and relaxed. Everything glided through smoothly. Luckily my teeth were in overall good shape. I plan to stick with them and was able to schedule my 6 month check up already. They're amazing!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
