{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Free street parking","enabled":true},{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true},{"name":"Paid street parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"John Anderson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocINFggeymmdxkCG4ki4dN2pwbJpjqZ51UQxE2Uh_VKSm-nkKQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very happy with Kola.  I was a patient of Dr. Lessner since he acquired the practice in the early 1990's.  When Dr. Kohlman took the practice over after Lessner's retirement, I wanted to wait before passing any judgement.\n\nI'm happy to report that Dr. Kohlman is a fantastic dentist - the best I've ever had.  He has the precision of an engineer and a razor-sharp attention to detail.  I've had 2 crowns from him and both involved no discomfort at all - perfectly executed.  He's well-versed on the latest technologies and methods.  I honestly feel fortunate to be in such great dental care.  The hygienists and other staff are top-notch as well - again, some of the best I've ever had.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Krystal Figueroa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVdsPuivHGhahH-8uTx415hIlrXlqWD2Svxb2lPIwkElmIBYDlV=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am so sad that my new insurance doesn't cover this clinic. KoLa dentistry has some of the best staff and most reasonable prices. They have always been transparent with me. They have done numerous cleanings, 2 wisdom teeth extractions, and permanent retainer repairs on me. Every visit I felt heard and taken care of. Definitely recommend this clinic to anyone looking for great care.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gerardo De Leon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWaYJzbRSjxphgN2oBz8jVaHDCYIR0pzS3b7z8WrPXLrAg5Ouc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Kola Family \u0026 Cosmetic Dentistry are extraordinary amazing in the manner in which they care for my spouse and me! As a customer service expert, I expect compassion, attentiveness, courtesy, and outcomes that connect to what matters most- not just as a consumer, patient, but as a human being! I travel from Dallas , Texas, to receive top-notch dental and human touch points from this exceptional care team that attends to my individual needs! Kola is not just my dentistry team, they are my family! If you are needing a family to love on you, give Kola a try! I know you will sing their praises as my spouse and I do! Thank you for the patient centric delivery: Cari, Angela, Kathy, Marissa, and Dr. Lalezari! You all are the best! I look forward to my crown replacement sprinkled by the sum of all the interactions of service you all own and deliver!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"drew","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLMHZ-AhVBN8XeORiRC0F9swMhZzqMFRoczPgM1QP4Vi6aSuXo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am not surprised there are so many good reviews. Dr. Kohlman and staff have done such excellent work that it inspired me to take better care of my teeth. To feel how much they care about helping people, has carried over into my life and has helped me not only with my teeth but in my attitude towards being aware and professional at my job. I don't mean to set the bar so high, because actually they are very grounded, and just take one day at a time.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Silo Newman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXXhCgL_OPPsJQHykduEPGorXC-thyDmhMfwChX9LmV6tMTgCWp=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I went in today for a routine cleaning and had such a pleasant experience. Marisa was my hygienist, and she was incredibly sweet, gentle, and easy to talk to, which really put me at ease. The cleaning was thorough but comfortable, and my teeth feel wonderful. It was just an all-around nice visit, and I truly appreciated the care and kindness I received. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Erik Zumalt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUm373DB7adf_21j14m9KkI2I7Pv9EelWGd6tAq96fXMNXM8EA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I always have a good experience with Kola Dentistry. Dr. Kohlman is always excellent and my new fillings already feel perfect.\n​Marie, my hygienist, is wonderful too. She made my recent cleaning totally stress-free. Thanks Y'all!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jan Austin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLSxSQj8tNunN4lfjsZcc0cGtMDz7eEf9Jzm-VBnr9N4mTPNg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Going to the dentist is not my favorite thing to do, but the folks at KoLa make it very pleasant. Thanks to lots of natural fluoride in the water in Amarillo, I have really good teeth. Because I really don't like for people to be doing anything in my mouth, I've taken good care of them and although they're not very pretty, they're very strong. My hygienist is delightful with a sincere interest in her patients. Make an appointment ASAP and have a great experience in the dentist's office - yeah, really!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Megan Conner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK4rMGrIogIWghKWgjKRIhz1Mq30D5BXv1tu1nwBuWBjsTq8Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love my hygienist, Dot. She's the best! My teeth are pretty boring, so I don't spend much time interacting with the dentist. He seems nice, though. The office staff are great, too.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
