umbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"103983026873377133711","name":"West Lake Hills Dental (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103983026873377133711"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Westlake Crossroads","street":"4105 Westbank Dr STE 103","city":"Austin","postal_code":"78746","state":"Texas","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible seating","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Cosmetic dentistry","enabled":true},{"name":"Emergency services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"P L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUCmozyY0y0TLJ7uWkoz8BxAxWGEcc4hDGOmf_udpVT9UflkWx4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love Westlake Dental! Cynthia and Lei are wonderful, not to mention Denise, Dr. Ronci, and Dr. Nguyen! I am not a huge fan of the dentist but they renewed my faith in comfortable cleanings and treatment. My husband and I have been patients for years and would not go anywhere else!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Doug Keenan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV-dxHsUaz1zCJ8M4NaS7eZ5fiMGhGSItQXAHGoul8Biaj0LceC=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our family has been a customer of this dental practice since the early 90s, through three (3) ownerships.  We have always had great dental care here, and my most recent experience was not different.  The practice has always kept up with technology and equipment to improve the care, as I noticed with my latest care.\nI experienced a chip from my #14, molar which had an old filling – so I needed a crown to repair it. I saw Dr. Kimberly Nguyen to proceed with her recommendation, having a temporary installed 1st, then the permanent porcelain one mounted on this past Monday (~3 weeks later during holiday time).  During the permanent install process, I experienced some high sensitivity to water and air.  But Dr. Nguyen and her assistant Rebecca were quick to remedy this with more anesthetic and finish.  The permanent crown feels great and has “0” sensitivity at all – feels great to bite and chew!\nThank you, Dr. Nguyen and Rebecca for your attention and help on this past Monday!  And let us not forget the front office staff, Lei and Christina, who helped me when I had the chipped molar occur.  They helped me navigating the very busy schedule of the practice during the holiday time.  Cheers!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Homero Gonzalez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKkktO62OdAvjCsyo110yjJ9CMPvtvbT_3IX39grjnmZBwRYg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been a patient for years. It’s a very friendly atmosphere. Lei and Cynthia are always very attentive. Joy is a very professional hygienist and makes me feel at ease. Dr. Ronci is very easy to talk to. He makes you feel like you’re part of his family. Wonderful staff!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lucitania Griffin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWOUA1J9pC9DRIbE1GYEl1tKY47bzFWQTwA3la0z-EW3DhkCdsEiw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"From the moment you walk in, the atmosphere is warm and welcoming. Every single member of the staff—from the front desk to the hygienists—is genuinely friendly and kind. They consistently go above and beyond. The entire team delivers exceptional patient care. I've been a patient for years and  can't imagine going anywhere else!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bryan Rumble","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKTYEsP4Myfe1JeBGyAWX-upgSLWBHspoY3zkNCMvubf3bU1g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"West Lake Hills is an EXCELLENT dental office.  They are friendly, professional, and very thorough in the care that they provide. On my last visit, Dr. Nguyen and Rebecca were very patient with me, helping to calm me during the procedure.  I strongly recommend this practice to anyone needing basic or extensive dental care.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bryan Sledge","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJYqYkGurPAjAOA4CGPQTezYuB9mW14S2OWJmZPoHK9j8jjTg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Ronci and Joy were amazing! They were very thorough and detailed oriented in making sure I got the best treatment. Couldn’t be happier with the service!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mary Tucker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX_d1cUhpgmmZnnCDLj4cgfdTYt8UpUIOnWMidZ3UUf_ZcRPewb=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Seriously, the best!  I'm so glad the retirement of my previous dentist required me to find a new dentist.  I have now visited with two of the doctors at West Lake Hills Dental and I can't recommend them enough.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Beth Asmussen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVQdV_lbfKMvi81Uqc9y-jtKoWp-hqrJpaiwWILVQPDTgr4aMyVxw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was way behind on my dental care and embarrassed. Everyone there made me feel welcome and were all so kind and patient with me.\nThey were very thorough and informative always asking if I had any questions.They thoroughly explained different options .\nI was pleasantly surprised at how wonderfully my dental visit went and would highly recommend West Lake Hills Dental ,great friendly staff ,Dr. Nguyen was very knowledgeable and gentle .","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
