LkrftAVw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went in to get a cleaning and get fitted for trays (I have clenching issues) and I got held up at work and they were EXTREMELY kind and understanding and even saw me anyways when I got there a little late, way better attitude then I was expecting considering I was late and being an inconvenience. They were even nice enough to make sure I was comfortable while getting scanned for my dental trays. I know my insurance isnt very good, but for the quality of my cleaning and how kind everyone was the price was more than worth it. Front desk, assistants, hygienists and doctors are all 10/10","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Corine Murat","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUcoxiqqF4iWqrQmC5rkaUzrMf7Io4uroejS91nlLZnoqA_Buj9qw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"GO TO DR. BERNAL! He is so good at what he does. He is such a great trustworthy dentist. He did crowns on my two front teeth and let these pictures speak for how amazing of a job he did. The two crowns match perfectly with my other teeth and I am constantly getting complimented on my teeth. No one can even tell they are crowns. I forget sometimes too :) ! Dr. Bernal made sure they were the perfect match before finalizing his work and I APPRECIATE him so much for this. GO TO HIM. TRUST ME.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn13q2nVwP8pIQ23sE3B3TLFCk_Xg4y8rToBH6kgOGag3VECXRWEvtXa89wSog2MBdYJhmHPrrEn0HZz9vL6bvMeu0bLUK_-04T6rVnf_YZR4Eltq67Ikt07l4A8mAQAkdzi7twz=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3OaoCU_WKlW7KweK-GdTWdqa-w5KgwMvvElP3niILcdNrP1fd5OhcFNlDVEsnRijBLXnyl32mzycDLO_gLU71BYRknc7N3yP8VW81xc8jEBmMG4GgeSdBna55cAii7V1fGarjPHA=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1Rbl5hvy0pK6vVlIupbmEYMJ_Ze1NN0J-whKhgtLbP9fcVJ5sbd2C1F9A2-kpTLU6AezhQ_WwbLHEQEllS9FQdcGshvIgnst24ihyRmY3qkeOCH4LULbyAFwCDFIAmtNNVWQfT=k-no"],"When":"2022-10-7"},{"Name":"Philippa Mason","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKh1seu71Hy_56pbsHzkX_vLUDrDAFcc9wfMILuXpfxXzH6gA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They did an AMAZING job on my cleaning - I was blown away by how white they got my teeth. I have always hated going to the dentist and I feel like a lot of dentists will shame you in one way or another and that was not the case here at all. The dentist and staff were really kind and warm and attentive. It was easy and quick to get an appointment too - I was able to book a cleaning as a new client only a few days out which I feel like can be rare!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL2wY1pGLBwEfGBdgBEmBr1J4q6LisktzuduECYWLZlyqjhBw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Going to the dentist for the past month and a half has been a terrible experience BUT the staff and the Doctor made this visit enjoyable. I only got an exam and xray but he took the time to actually speak to me and educate me. I’m excited to get work done here in the future!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Katrina O Day","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIZ7scU0XCAtRNFKEn8kbW3KwhXp832wmuaIgw-XM0z_wKBmg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place has the most amazing staff all across the board! I drive over 80 miles for my check ups and cleanings because of the comforting service I receive. They put my dental anxiety to rest. As soon as I get in the chair I know I am in good hands!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Camille Gan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXgqlm5DCPX7O40HP7_HtZN9Q866TLlnRUhhT7OIvKpszWnoc2nmw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Potter and the staff are outstanding! They take their time to explain everything in details and make you feel so comfortable no matter if the issue is big or small. Amazing experience every time. Highly recommend!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gras