complete a reassuring evaluation. It does not get much better than this for attentive quality care for a stranger in a city.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michael Ovalle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUD0r6kX4GYF-99lUXMzOGt4IfDofb8axBYtGifDlJIIxrAeB2eag=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"nice and friendly staff. they've got all the tech for digital imaging and offer many services. my one stop shop for all things dental. they also have an app to monitor your dental health and for scheduling appointments.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hallie Lucas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK2lVS_frzGqYHIK9tcpBlT-FQO2zsXFaFyApMiROhBhJ-k4A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had my cleaning today and I had a great experience! Specifically my dental hygienist, Talia, was sooo kind and personable! She made me feel at ease. Usually I am super anxious at the dentist but even my blood pressure was normal (which is crazy for me! lol) thank you Talia for making it a very smooth process! I’ll be back :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cesar Munoz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLWByLpZLfZ5Mt54mbxhyjITkrdjt-wWKpwz_miQzAWzl429Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jax was my dental hygienist (she was super sweet and informative throughout the appointment) Dr. Sirage was whom reviewed my xray. He was awesome. Both were absolutely amazing and the front staff is too! The lobby is super cozy and the overall place has great energy.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Andrea Angiolini","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW7IAIK1UuiMoWoPCmZqHv87txWQPQ_LDaJXsFreCMVUS6MGCY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Enjoyed the visit until the end where they stuck me in a room and tried to get me to pay a deposit for veneers on my next visit. The lady literally signed the forms for me until I had to tell her to cancel it because the fine print said deposit was non refundable. I felt it was honestly good up until that point, I really liked my hygienist Jax - she was super nice and genuine.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Koby Ramirez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLhjM_nAVNRN3mA7TXPl_nZLCw99paYGUfCgPPCPh06SaxHJg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I don’t write much reviews, but wanted to share my experience at breeze! They have been so helpful through out my time here. When I first moved to Austin I was unsure of where to go for Invisalign treatment, and luckily I found my way to Breeze! They have been extremely patient with me, accommodating, non-judgmental, and most importantly trustworthy! I’m done with my Invisalign treatment now, and my teeth have never looked better! Huge thank you to the whole breeze team, I highly recommend them!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Maria Gallardo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLZDPrD9dpklp1fB4119jqmJMl5u2zNOCKyItVYZ29AHQgFHQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Was very pleasant. All staff were very friendly and welcoming. They were very informative about my what I needed done. The doctor was polite and helpful. Thank you for your courtesy.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
