yment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Free street parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Samuel Perez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ_sQpEWde_iAu6-7zG6CD1TJ1yObUTzCDf2F7F8Idar82wLQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Disappointing experience at Swish on 4th. I went in for a routine cleaning at 10:00 AM and didn’t leave until 11:51 AM — nearly two hours for a basic cleaning is unacceptable.\n\nThey were clearly short-staffed, with only one dentist and not enough hygienists for the number of patients scheduled. The staff kept apologizing and thanking me for my patience, which I appreciate, but apologies do not fix the issue.\n\nIf you know you’re understaffed, you shouldn’t schedule so many appointments at once. Better scheduling and management would make a big difference. Unfortunately, this missed the mark.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tiffany Wooten","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXnooOKJYMlE1wIoVNQuJyVCiABzDRF3Ry9zBTNFedWShpGqx8c=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Everyone at Swish is always amazing. They are welcoming, seeming to genuinely care about us and how we are. They remember our family, share kind words and compliments, and are very professional. They’ve never made any of our family of 4 feel anything but kindness and calm, which is not easy for a dentist! Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"M C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIbvMA00y-UUuCuxtN6yv1MO8agAsP7diL8mGX6oXECkRNm=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Both my hygienist, bless her heart, she had a tough job on my teeth, it had been too long, and the doctor were excellent. They couldn’t have been more knowledgeable or accommodating. Bedside manner and professionalism were exactly as one would hope for. Forgive me I don’t have their names with me, but my initials are C.M. and my appointment was earlier today at 2pm  E 4th st location.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Andrea Jaquez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUVEyEieW22B4rfjFOjuBrw6M9xl53KytLJABD-W0RfNnFW_vyrqA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Springer and Yusuf were so so friendly and great! I had to get a tooth that has chipped too many times filled again which is usually long and uncomfortable. They got it done super quick and easy and the results look great!\n\nI went here after having a bad experience at the Brodie location and I couldn’t recommend this location more. The entire team was very communicative, friendly, professional, and made everything simple from start to finish. Definitely recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Paula De La Torre","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXEP63QZe4lY2My7JCGMSjfH-grpqHZcQjJyjCGfJ3YQCYG13Y=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I went to the Swish Dental East 4th location and my visit was easy and efficient! Tyler was incredible. He helped me book the appointment and made me feel so comfortable. Also shout out to the other staff, everyone at this office was so sweet. I can’t wait for my next visit.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Elena Marez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWrsBtlKWydE-tdvQMDwRGkjQVf0qD4bQvm6IoP7QaZg_z9wf1Zlg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The surgical team were kind and professional. They made my wisdom teeth removal stress-free and as comfortable as possible. Would definitely recommend all the ladies at the Swish Dental on 4th!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"William Grimes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWWldItQS27abccq9WgnBThnOpBzYgt3y0jEXaiPLGoyo7df5Y1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"2nd location of swish that I’ve even to. Team is always friendly and welcoming. As scary as dental visits go they go out of their way to making you feel as comfortable as possible.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chad Lanfer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUeOOL7UgpNPi9cNjdme-Cs1-myNxODqJVDeBkep9k19wCJexBz=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a procedure and have really sensitive teeth. Very nervous of the dentist and Dr. Laurie and Yusuf were above and beyond such a treat and did a very very good job. Made me feel comfortable, at ease and ultimately saved a tooth from a root canal. The only place I’m going from here on out in Austin.\n\nThank you Laurie and Yusuf :)","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
