ded","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Deni Vidaurri","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV9cDVM1iU7RkfkloNeJNzIlsC5GVM1HmtkTBsZ6GJ0T-DRhCI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My bad fortune brought me to High Point Dentistry (tooth pain!), but it is my very good fortune to have found Dr. Lau!  As a very traumatized dental patient from previous experiences, I was so anxious to not only need immediate relief and dental work, but I also did so at the same time I realized I needed a new dentist. Really bad timing. But I am SO GRATEFUL to have found this practice.\n\nDr. Lau shows his expertise by being so informative about the what, why and how of the work needed.  He is so very empathetic and supportive, as is his staff. They constantly check in to ensure I'm comfortable at all times.  Today, I received a crown replacement, and the whole experience was a huge departure from all the anxiety I have carried about seeing dentists.  I wish I had a dentist like Dr. Lau when I was younger, and if I had, I'm sure I wouldn't be so angst-ridden now!  Also, his staff is wonderful and kind, and the front-office is very accommodating at scheduling and billing.\n\nIf you are looking for a new dentist (or even if you're not), you couldn't find a better dentist!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jessica Wood","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV3bnwtLbDqsrHHIIGt5I0yU9PtAu1Oh-SVsbQpb2gS4wcuDy2a=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been coming to this Westgate location for over twenty years, and have to give a shoutout to the incredibly skilled and kind Dr. Lau. I am very attached to his predecessor, Dr. Yarbrough, so I’m especially grateful at how carefully the practice is transitioning to keep up the impeccable quality of work, and warm culture of friendship that is a signature of this office. Such good people!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Beth Marshall","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW2wkvh-B-Mxy1BRzoD0cCY427mOAMPjjLDa-e1FLnuy7IJWkA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve had nothing but positive experiences at the Westgate location of High Point Dentistry. After skipping the dentist for years and developing some dental anxiety, they have made me feel so comfortable over my last few visits with them. Dr. Lau is so personable and explains things in a way I can understand, and every dental hygienist I’ve had there is professional and kind. So glad to have them as my neighborhood dentist office!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lily Sanders","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVkaCSekCxzbBJyg7dCo26A8QF39vRHYKkGvSkdyxO0sB9o00mn=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Service is always great. From the front desk, to the hygienist (shoutout Holly!), all the way to the doctor. Thank you guys for caring for all your patients and making time to answer every question and give ample resources.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"shawn crum","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLhd9vEny-YMf14HbVsNlRjZAgGhLsQ_5X-kI2E_C6imdek6A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came in for a crown replacement and I’m completely blown away by the incredible service here. Everybody is very personable and they really go above and beyond to make you feel comeortable. Thankful to have found a dentist that I’m actually excited to go to.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Carla Rodon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVq5MRSyHLyJ83yVQ34N1fCOvG9E3GDm1B2AvtUhw0HthnZP1M=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came here for several procedures after braces treatment. Everything has been top notch, from the procedures to the environment. Everyone, from the front desk to the doctors in the back, are very kind and knowledgeable. 10/10 🩷","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gary Manche","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUaBc3gRuU6FC0p2PYBHC8svOHgQkedpqzxHj6F45Zzt4cRAgA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My first visit here and certainly the best dentist experience ever. The support staff was friendly and professional, Dr. Lau was very thorough in his examination and found a potential area of oncoming decay. I’m looking forward to resolving this in the near future and feel very confident in the care provided by the High Point team.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Terri Fenner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUe-N2ePqU8wmAc3tqd3HyOKqjwrN0SGr-_4SglOi7VW1dFPQ_V=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Have been to other dentists but always return to Dr. Y, who is trying to retire. I have seen 2 different dentists since new owners. Amazing reception and dentists who are not high pressure. They listened to my concerns and hope for future dental plan. Cost is worth it for the expert care with best listening by the staff and doctors. I’m finished roaming to other places for many reasons. My forever dental office.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
